(197, 'heimerdinger-h-28g-evolution-turret.png', '', ' Cooldown: 1<br />Cost: 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110<br />Range: 250<br />Heimerdinger constructs a Machine Gun Turret with (260 + 21 x Lvl) health that does 30 / 38 / 46 / 54 / 62 (+20% of ability power) magic damage. Turrets attack 50% faster the first 6 seconds. Turrets will only deal half damage to towers and inhibitors. Max: 1 / 1 / 2 / 2 / 2 Turrets.<br /><br />Every level of this skill will level the turret into a new type, becoming a green armor and magic resist reducing turret (1 reduction per hit up to 50 stacks) at level 2, the ability to place up to 2 turrets at level 3, 125 bonus health for his turrets at level 4 and a red area of effect attacker at level 5.<br /><br />Heimerdinger gains a &quot;Stockpiled H-28G Evolution Turret&quot; charge every 25 seconds. Max 1 / 1 / 2 / 2 / 2 charges.', '', 'H-28G Evolution Turret', 'Sobafire.com'),
