(225, 'gragas-barrel-roll.png', '', ' Cooldown: 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7<br />Cost: 80 / 90 / 100 / 110 / 120<br />Range: 1100<br />Gragas rolls his cask to a target location, which can be activated again to explode after arriving or will explode on its own after 5 seconds, dealing 85 / 135 / 185 / 235 / 285 (+90% of ability power) damage and slowing the attack speed of enemies struck by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 % for 3 seconds.', '', 'Barrel Roll', 'Sobafire.com'),
(226, 'gragas-drunken-rage.png', '', ' Cooldown: 25<br /><br />Gragas guzzles down brew from his cask, channeling for 1 second. He gains 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 mana while channeling, and becomes empowered after finishing, increasing his attack damage by 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70, and reducing damage taken by 10 / 12 / 14 / 16 / 18% for 20 seconds.', '', 'Drunken Rage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(227, 'gragas-body-slam.png', '', ' Cooldown: 7<br />Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70<br />Range: 650<br />Gragas charges forward with a charge speed of 650 / 750 / 850 / 950 / 1050, colliding with the first enemy unit he hits and dealing 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 (+50% of ability power) (plus 0.66 per attack damage) to enemies in the area. Damage is split amongst targets hit, minimum 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150 damage. Units hit by Body Slam are slowed by 35% for 2.5 seconds.', '', 'Body Slam', 'Sobafire.com'),
(228, 'gragas-explosive-cask.png', '', ' Cooldown: 90 / 75 / 60<br />Cost: 100 / 125 / 150<br />Range: 1050<br />Gragas throws his cask to a location, which explodes on impact, dealing 200 / 325 / 450 (+100% of ability power) magic damage to all units struck, knocking them back.', '', 'Explosive Cask', 'Sobafire.com'),
(229, 'mordekaiser-iron-man.png', '', ' 30% of the damage dealt from abilities is converted into a temporary shield, absorbing incoming damage. Shield generation is only half as effective against minions. Maximum shield strength is 90 + (30 x level). The shield decays by 3% per second. ', '', 'Iron Man', 'Sobafire.com'),
(230, 'mordekaiser-mace-of-spades.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 / 4<br />Cost: 25 / 32 / 39 / 46 / 53<br />Range: 600<br />On next hit, Mordekaiser swings his mace with such force that it echoes out, striking up to 3 additional nearby targets, dealing 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 / 200 (+1 per bonus attack damage) (+40% of ability power) magic damage.If the target is alone, the ability deals 65% more damage.', '', 'Mace of Spades', 'Sobafire.com'),
(231, 'mordekaiser-creeping-death.png', '', ' Cooldown: 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12<br />Cost: 26 / 32 / 38 / 44 / 50<br />Range: 750<br />Unleashes a protective cloud of metal shards to surround an ally or himself, increasing their armor and magic resistance by 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 and dealing 24 / 38 / 52 / 66 / 80 (+20% of ability power) damage per second to enemies in the cloud for 6 seconds.', '', 'Creeping Death', 'Sobafire.com'),
(232, 'mordekaiser-siphon-of-destruction.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6<br />Cost: 24 / 36 / 48 / 60 / 72<br />Range: 700<br />Mordekaiser damages enemies in a cone in front of him, dealing 65 / 105 / 145 / 185 / 225 (+60% of ability power) magic damage.', '', 'Siphon of Destruction', 'Sobafire.com'),
(233, 'mordekaiser-children-of-the-grave.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120 / 105 / 90<br />Range: 850<br />Mordekaiser deals an initial 12 / 14.5 / 17 (+2% of ability power) % magic damage equal to that percentage of the target&acute;s maximum health and curses it for 10 seconds.During these 10 seconds, 1.2 / 1.45 / 1.7 (+2% of ability power) % magic damage equal to that percentage of the target&acute;s maximum health per second is dealt.<br /><br />If the target dies while under the effect of the curse, their soul is enslaved and will follow Mordekaiser for 30 seconds. During this time, Mordekaiser gains 20% of their ability power, and attack damage. The spirit gains 75% of Mordekaiser&acute;s adjusted damage, ability power, and health totals.<br /><br />Pets can be controlled by holding the alt key and using the right mouse button.', '', 'Children of the Grave', 'Sobafire.com'),
(234, 'ezreal-rising-spell-force.png', '', ' Hitting a target with any of Ezreal&acute;s abilities increases his attack speed by 10% for 6 seconds, stacking up to 5 times.', '', 'Rising Spell Force', 'Sobafire.com'),
(235, 'ezreal-mystic-shot.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6 / 5.5 / 5 / 4.5 / 4<br />Cost: 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50<br />Range: 1000<br />Ezreal fires a bolt of energy that deals 35 / 55 / 75 / 95 / 115 (+1.0 per attack damage) (+20% of ability power) physical damage and applies on-hit effects. If it strikes an enemy unit it reduces all of Ezreal&acute;s cooldowns by 1 second.', '', 'Mystic Shot', 'Sobafire.com'),
(236, 'ezreal-essence-flux.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9<br />Cost: 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100<br />Range: 900<br />Ezreal fires a fluctuating wave of energy at a targeted area. Any enemy champions it passes through take 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280 (+70% of ability power) magic damage and have their attack speed slowed by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 5 seconds, while any allied champions it travels through have their attack speed increased by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 5 seconds.', '', 'Essence Flux', 'Sobafire.com'),
(237, 'ezreal-arcane-shift.png', '', ' Cooldown: 19 / 17 / 15 / 13 / 11<br />Cost: 90<br />Range: 475<br />Ezreal teleports to a target nearby location and fires a homing arrow at the nearest enemy unit dealing 75 / 125 / 175 / 225 / 275 (+75% of ability power) magic damage.', '', 'Arcane Shift', 'Sobafire.com'),
(238, 'ezreal-trueshot-barrage.png', '', ' Cooldown: 80<br />Cost: 150<br />Range: 20000<br />Ezreal channels for 1 second to fire a powerful barrage of energy missiles, which deal 350 / 500 / 650 (+1.0 per bonus attack damage) (+90% of ability power) magic damage to each enemy unit they pass through. However, it deals 8% less damage for each unit it hits (30% minimum damage).', '', 'Trueshot Barrage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(239, 'shen-ki-strike.png', '', ' Every 8 seconds, Shen&acute;s next attack deals 5+5*level+8% of his bonus health as extra magic damage. Whenever an enemy champion hits Shen with a basic attack, the cooldown is reduced by 2 seconds.', '', 'Ki Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(240, 'shen-vorpal-blade.png', '', ' Cooldown: 3<br />Cost: 70 / 65 / 60 / 55 / 50<br />Range: 475<br />Deals 70 / 115 / 140 / 175 / 210 (+75% of ability power) magic damage to target unit. That unit becomes life tapped for 5 seconds, healing any champions who attack it for 18 / 26 / 34 / 42 / 50 health over 3 seconds.', '', 'Vorpal Blade', 'Sobafire.com'),
(241, 'shen-feint.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5<br />Cost: 45<br /><br />Shen enters a defensive stance, shielding the next 50 / 100 / 150 / 200 / 250 (+75% of ability power) damage. Lasts up to 2.5 seconds or until it is destroyed.', '', 'Feint', 'Sobafire.com'),
(242, 'shen-shadow-dash.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 120 / 115 / 110 / 105 / 100<br />Range: 600<br />Shen rapidly dashes to a target location, Taunting enemies he collides with for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 second(s).<br /><br />Restores 50 Energy if you collide with a champion.', '', 'Shadow Dash', 'Sobafire.com'),
(243, 'shen-stand-united.png', '', ' Cooldown: 180 / 150 / 120<br /><br />Places a shield on a target allied champion, absorbing 200 / 475 / 750 (+150% of ability power) damage for 7.5 seconds. After channeling for 2.5 seconds, Shen teleports to the target&acute;s location.', '', 'Stand United', 'Sobafire.com'),
(244, 'kennen-mark-of-the-storm.png', '', ' Kennen&acute;s abilities add Marks of the Storm to opponents which last for 8 seconds. An opponent is stunned for 1 second upon receiving 3 Marks of the Storm. Also, Kennen receives 25 energy. The stun has a diminished effect if applied more than once within 7 seconds. ', '', 'Mark of the Storm', 'Sobafire.com'),
(245, 'kennen-thundering-shuriken.png', '', ' Cooldown: 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 / 3<br />Cost: 65 / 60 / 55 / 50 / 45<br />Range: 900<br />Kennen throws a fast moving shuriken towards a location, dealing 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235 (+75% of ability power) magic damage and adding a Mark of the Storm to any opponent that it hits.', '', 'Thundering Shuriken', 'Sobafire.com'),
(246, 'kennen-electrical-surge.png', '', ' Cooldown: 14 / 12 / 10 / 8 / 6<br />Cost: 45<br />Range: 800<br />(Passive): Every 5 attacks, Kennen deals magic damage equal to 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80% of his attack damage and adds a Mark of the Storm to his target.<br /><br />(Active): Surges electricity through all nearby targets afflicted by Mark of the Storm, dealing 65 / 95 / 125 / 155 / 185 (+55% of ability power) magic damage and adding another mark.', '', 'Electrical Surge', 'Sobafire.com'),
(247, 'kennen-lightning-rush.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6<br />Cost: 100 / 95 / 90 / 85 / 80<br />Range: 20<br />Kennen gains his base movement speed again as a flat movement speed bonus, as well as 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 increased Armor and Magic Resistance, and the ability to pass through units for four seconds, but he is unable to attack. Lightning Rush deals 85 / 125 / 165 / 205 / 245 (+60% of ability power) magic damage and adds a Mark of the Storm to any hostile unit he passes through; deals half damage to minions.<br /><br />Kennen is refunded 40 energy if he passes through an enemy while using this spell, but can only gain this effect once. ', '', 'Lightning Rush', 'Sobafire.com'),
(248, 'kennen-slicing-maelstrom.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120<br />Cost: 50 / 45 / 40<br />Range: 550<br />Kennen summons a magical storm that deals 80 / 145 / 210 (+40% of ability power) magic damage to a random enemy champion near Kennen every few seconds. The storm hits 6 / 10 / 15 times with a 0.5 / 0.4 / 0.33 second delay between each bolt, and cannot hit the same target more than 3 times. A Mark of the Storm is applied to enemies each time they are hit.', '', 'Slicing Maelstrom', 'Sobafire.com'),
(249, 'akali-twin-disciplines.png', 'Akali 20 AP topladığı zaman vuruşları %8 bonus büyü hasarı vermekte olup, 20 AP´nin üzerindeki her 6 AP için, bu oran %1 artacaktır. (Büyü hasarının kuleler üzerinde bir etkisi yoktur.)<br><br>\r\n\r\nAkali 10 AD topladığı zaman vuruşları 8% Spell Vamp bonusuna sahip olup, 10 AD´nin üzerindeki her 6 AD için bu oran %1 artacaktır.', 'Upon obtaining 20 ability power, Akali&acute;s hits deal 8% bonus magic damage, increasing by 1% for every 6 ability power gained thereafter. (Magic damage doesn&acute;t affect towers, but it affects other structures.) <br /><br />Upon obtaining 10 attack damage, Akali gains 8% Spell Vamp, increasing by an additional 1% for every 6 attack damage gained thereafter.', 'Çifte Disiplin', 'Twin Disciplines', 'Sobafire.com'),
(250, 'akali-mark-of-the-assassin.png', 'Süre: 6 / 5.5 / 5 / 4.5 / 4<br>\r\nMaliyet: 60<br>\r\nMesafe: 600<br>\r\nAkali kamasını bir düşman ünitesine fırlatır ve 45 / 70 / 95 / 120 / 145 (+40% büyü gücü) büyü hasarı verir. Bu büyü düşmanı 6 saniye boyunca işaretler.<br><br>\r\n\r\nAkali´nin normal saldırıları işareti parçalayıp 45 / 70 / 95 / 120 / 145 (+40% büyü gücü) oranında büyü hasarı verir ve Akali''ye 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 değerinde enerjiyi geri kazandırır. ', ' Cooldown: 6 / 5.5 / 5 / 4.5 / 4<br />Cost: 60<br />Range: 600<br />Akali spins her kama at a target enemy to deal 45 / 70 / 95 / 120 / 145 (+40% of ability power) magic damage and mark the target for 6 seconds.<br /><br />Akali&acute;s melee attacks against a marked target will trigger and consume the mark to cause 45 / 70 / 95 / 120 / 145 (+40% of ability power) magic damage and restore 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 energy.', 'Suikastçinin İşareti', 'Mark of the Assassin', 'Sobafire.com'),
(251, 'akali-twilight-shroud.png', 'Süre: 20<br>\r\nMaliyet: 80 / 75 / 70 / 65 / 60<br>\r\nMesafe: 700<br>\r\nAkali 8 saniyeliğine dumandan bir alan yaratır. Alanın içine girdiğinde Akali 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 armor ve büyü direnci kazanır. Akali duman içerisinde kaldığı süre boyunca görünmez olur. Yetenek kullandığı takdirde görünmezliği biter. <br><br>\r\nBu alanın içine giren düşmanlar 14 / 18 / 22 / 26 / 30% oranında yavaşlar.', 'Cooldown: 20<br />Cost: 80 / 75 / 70 / 65 / 60<br />Range: 700<br />Akali throws down a cover of smoke that lasts for 8 seconds. While inside the area, Akali gains 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 armor and magic resist and becomes stealthed. Attacking or using abilities will briefly reveal her.<br /><br />Enemies inside the smoke have their movement speed reduced by 14 / 18 / 22 / 26 / 30%.', 'Alacakaranlık Örtüsü', 'Twilight Shroud', 'Sobafire.com'),
(252, 'akali-crescent-slash.png', 'Süre: 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 / 3<br>\r\nMaliyet: 60<br>\r\nMesafe: 325<br>\r\nAkali kamalarını etrafında döndürür ve düşmanlarına 30 / 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 (+30 büyü gücü) + (60% fiziksel güç) oranında fiziksel hasar verir. ', ' Cooldown: 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 / 3<br />Cost: 60<br />Range: 325<br />Akali flourishes her kamas, hitting nearby units for 30 / 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 physical damage (+30% of ability power) + 60% Attack Damage.', 'Hilal Vuruşu', 'Crescent Slash', 'Sobafire.com'),
(253, 'akali-shadow-dance.png', 'Bekleme Süresi: 2 / 1.5 / 1<br>\r\nMesafe: 800<br>\r\nAkali hedefine çok hızlı bir biçimde saldırır ve 100 / 175 / 250 (+50% büyü gücü) büyü hasarı verir.<br><br>\r\n\r\nAkali öldürdüğü veya kazandığı her asist sonucunda 1 stack kazanır. Her bir stackın bekleme süresi 25 / 20 / 15 saniyedir. Maximum 3 stack yapılabilir.', ' Cooldown: 2 / 1.5 / 1<br />Range: 800<br />Akali moves through shadows to quickly strike her target, dealing 100 / 175 / 250 (+50% of ability power) magic damage.<br /><br />Akali stores an Essence of Shadow on kills and assists as well as every 25 / 20 / 15 seconds up to 3 total.', 'Gölge Dansı', 'Shadow Dance', 'Sobafire.com'),
(254, 'garen-perseverance.png', '', ' Garen regenerates 0.5% of his maximum health per second after not receiving or dealing damage for 7 seconds.', '', 'Perseverance', 'Sobafire.com'),
(255, 'garen-decisive-strike.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8<br />Range: 300<br />Garen gains 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35% movement speed for 4 seconds. His next melee attack within 6 seconds will deal 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 (+1.4 per attack damage) physical damage and silence his target for 2.5 seconds. ', '', 'Decisive Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(256, 'garen-courage.png', '', ' Cooldown: 30 / 27 / 24 / 21 / 18<br />Range: 20<br />(Passive): Garen&acute;s armor and magic resistance are permanently increased by 0.5 every time he kills an enemy unit (maximum 25) additional armor and magic resist)<br /><br />(Active): Garen places a defensive shield on himself, decreasing all damage taken by 20 / 24 / 28 / 32 / 36% for 3 seconds.', '', 'Courage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(257, 'garen-judgment.png', '', ' Cooldown: 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9<br />Range: 330<br />Garen rapidly spins his sword around his body for 3 seconds, removing all existing slows and reducing the duration of new slows by 50%, and dealing 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210 (+1.4 per bonus Attack Damage) physical damage to nearby enemies every second.<br /><br />Damage to minions is reduced by 50%.', '', 'Judgment', 'Sobafire.com'),
(258, 'garen-demacian-justice.png', '', ' Cooldown: 140 / 120 / 100<br />Range: 400<br />Garen brings down Demacian Justice on his opponent, dealing 175 / 350 / 525 magic damage plus 1 additional damage per 3.5 / 3 / 2.5 health his opponent is missing.', '', 'Demacian Justice', 'Sobafire.com'),
(259, 'malzahar-summon-voidling.png', '', ' After casting 4 spells, Malzahar summons an uncontrollable Voidling to engage enemy units for 21 seconds. Voidlings have 200 + 50 x lvl Health and 20 + 5 x lvl Damage.<br /><br />Voidlings Grow after 7 seconds (+50% Damage/Armor), and Frenzy after 14 seconds (+100% Attack Speed).<br /><br />Voidlings attack the target affected by Malzahar&acute;s most recently cast Malefic Visions.', '', 'Summon Voidling', 'Sobafire.com'),
(260, 'malzahar-call-of-the-void.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9<br />Cost: 80 / 90 / 100 / 110 / 120<br />Range: 900<br />Malzahar opens two portals to the void. After a short delay, they fire projectiles which deal 80 / 135 / 190 / 245 / 300 (+80% of ability power) magic damage and silence champions for 1.4 / 1.8 / 2.2 / 2.6 / 3 seconds.', '', 'Call of the Void', 'Sobafire.com'),
(261, 'malzahar-null-zone.png', '', ' Cooldown: 14<br />Cost: 90 / 100 / 110 / 120 / 130<br />Range: 800<br />Malzahar creates a zone of negative energy for 5 seconds. The zone deals 4 / 5 / 6 / 7 / 8% (+1% of ability power)% of the target&acute;s max health as magic damage each second (damage to monsters is capped).', '', 'Null Zone', 'Sobafire.com'),
(262, 'malzahar-malefic-visions.png', '', ' Cooldown: 15 / 13 / 11 / 9 / 7<br />Cost: 60 / 75 / 90 / 105 / 120<br />Range: 650<br />Malzahar infects his target&acute;s mind, dealing 80 / 140 / 200 / 260 / 320 (+80% of ability power) magic damage over 4 seconds. If the target dies during this time, the visions pass to a nearby enemy and Malzahar gains 10 / 14 / 18 / 22 / 26 mana. Malzahar&acute;s Voidlings are attracted to affected units.', '', 'Malefic Visions', 'Sobafire.com'),
(263, 'malzahar-nether-grasp.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120 / 100 / 80<br />Cost: 150<br />Range: 700<br />Malzahar grips his target in an engulfing void of energy to suppress the target (stuns and disables summoner spells), dealing 250 / 400 / 550 (+130% of ability power) magic damage over 2.5 seconds.The damage is applied in ticks, every half second.', '', 'Nether Grasp', 'Sobafire.com'),
(264, 'olaf-berzerker-rage.png', '', ' For each 1% of health missing, Olaf&acute;s attack speed is increased by 1%.', '', 'Berzerker Rage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(265, 'olaf-undertow.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 / 75<br />Range: 1000<br />Olaf throws an axe to a target location, dealing 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210 (+0.5 per attack damage) physical damage to units it passes through and slowing them by 24 / 28 / 32 / 36 / 40% for 2.5 seconds.<br /><br />If Olaf picks up the axe, the ability&acute;s cooldown is reduced by 6 seconds.', '', 'Undertow', 'Sobafire.com'),
(266, 'olaf-vicious-strikes.png', '', ' Cost: 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60<br />Range: 700<br />For 6 seconds, Olaf&acute;s attack damage is increased by 7 / 14 / 21 / 28 / 35 base damage plus 1% of his max health. While active, Olaf gains 9 / 12 / 15 / 18 / 21% lifesteal and spell vamp.', '', 'Vicious Strikes', 'Sobafire.com'),
(267, 'olaf-reckless-swing.png', '', ' Range: 325<br />Olaf deals 100 / 160 / 220 / 280 / 340 true damage to his target and inflicts 40 / 64 / 88 / 112 / 136 true damage to himself.', '', 'Reckless Swing', 'Sobafire.com'),
(268, 'olaf-ragnarok.png', '', ' Cost: 100 / 75 / 50<br />Range: 400<br />Active: Breaks any crowd control effects. For 6 seconds, Olaf is immune to disables and reduces incoming damage by 20 / 30 / 40.<br /><br />Passive: Olaf has 10 / 20 / 30 increased armor penetration.', '', 'Ragnarok', 'Sobafire.com'),
(269, 'kogmaw-icathian-surprise.png', '', ' Upon dying, Kog&acute;Maw starts a chain reaction in his body which causes him to move faster and detonate after 4 seconds; dealing 100 + (25 x lvl) true damage to surrounding enemies.', '', 'Icathian Surprise', 'Sobafire.com'),
(270, 'kogmaw-caustic-spittle.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8<br />Cost: 60<br />Range: 625<br />Passive: Increases attack speed by 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30%<br /><br />Active: Kog&acute;Maw launches a corrosive projectile which deals 60 / 110 / 160 / 210 / 260 (+70% of ability power) magic damage and reduces the target&acute;s armor and magic resist by 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 and for 4 seconds.', '', 'Caustic Spittle', 'Sobafire.com'),
(271, 'kogmaw-bio-arcane-barrage.png', '', ' Cooldown: 17<br />Cost: 50<br />Range: 130 / 150 / 170 / 190 / 210<br />Kog&acute;Maw&acute;s attacks gain 130 / 150 / 170 / 190 / 210 range and deal an additional 2 / 3 / 4 / 5 / 6 % (+1% per 100 ability power) of the target&acute;s maximum Health as Magic Damage (Max: 100 Damage vs Monsters). Lasts 8 seconds.', '', 'Bio-Arcane Barrage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(272, 'kogmaw-void-ooze.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12<br />Cost: 80 / 90 / 100 / 110 / 120<br />Range: 1000<br />Kog&acute;Maw launches ooze which deals 60 / 110 / 160 / 210 / 260 (+70% of ability power) magic damage to enemies it passes through.<br /><br />Additionally, it leaves a trail which slows enemies by 28 / 36 / 44 / 52 / 60% for 4 seconds.', '', 'Void Ooze', 'Sobafire.com'),
(273, 'kogmaw-living-artillery.png', '', ' Cooldown: 2 / 1.5 / 1<br />Cost: 40<br />Range: 1400 / 1700 / 2000<br />Kog&acute;Maw fires artillery from a great distance. After a short delay, the artillery falls dealing 80 / 120 / 160 + (+30% of ability power) and (+50% bonus attack damage) magic damage and reveals targets for 4 seconds (deals 250% bonus damage to Champions). Each subsequent Living Artillery in the next 6 seconds costs 40 additional mana (Max 200).', '', 'Living Artillery', 'Sobafire.com'),
(274, 'xin-zhao-tireless-warrior.png', '', ' Xin Zhao is healed for 30 points for every 3 attacks that he lands. This amount increases by 5 every 2 levels.', '', 'Tireless Warrior', 'Sobafire.com'),
(275, 'xin-zhao-three-talon-strike.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 30<br />Range: 375<br />Xin Zhao prepares to unleash a fearsome combo, causing his next 3 standard attacks to deal his attack damage + 15 / 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 to enemy targets, with the final attack knocking his opponent into the air.', '', 'Three Talon Strike', 'Sobafire.com');
INSERT INTO `lol_skills` (`SkillNum`, `imgPath`, `TR`, `EN`, `TR_skillname`, `EN_skillname`, `Cevirmen`) VALUES
(276, 'xin-zhao-battle-cry.png', '', ' Cooldown: 24 / 22 / 20 / 18 / 16<br />Cost: 35<br /><br />(Passive): Xin Zhao passively increases his attack speed by20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 %.<br /><br />(Active): Xin Zhao unleashes a battle cry, increasing his attack speed by passive amount again for 5 seconds, and causing his standard attacks during this time to reduce all of his other abilities&acute; cooldowns by 1 second.', '', 'Battle Cry', 'Sobafire.com'),
(277, 'xin-zhao-audacious-charge.png', '', ' Cooldown: 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12<br />Cost: 70<br />Range: 650<br />Xin Zhao charges an enemy unit, dealing 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 (+40% of ability power) damage to all nearby enemies and slowing them by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 % for 1.5 seconds.', '', 'Audacious Charge', 'Sobafire.com'),
(278, 'xin-zhao-crescent-sweep.png', '', ' Cost: 100<br />Range: 20<br />Xin Zhao unleashes a fierce spear sweep on targets around him, dealing 125 / 225 / 325 + 20% of their current health in physical damage. His magic resistance and armor are increased by 30 / 40 / 50 for the next 6 seconds.', '', 'Crescent Sweep', 'Sobafire.com'),
(284, 'vladimir-crimson-pact.png', '', ' Every 40 points of bonus health gives Vladimir 1 ability power and every 1 point of ability power gives Vladimir 1.8 bonus health. This bonuses do not stack with themselves.', '', 'Crimson Pact', 'Sobafire.com'),
(285, 'vladimir-transfusion.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12 / 10 / 8 / 6 / 4<br />Range: 600<br />Vladimir drains the lifeforce of his target, dealing 90 / 125 / 160 / 195 / 230 (+60% of ability power) magic damage and healing himself for 15 / 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 (+25% of ability power).', '', 'Transfusion', 'Sobafire.com'),
(286, 'vladimir-sanguine-pool.png', '', ' Cooldown: 26 / 23 / 20 / 17 / 13<br />Cost: 20<br />Range: 300<br />Vladimir sinks into a pool of blood for 2 seconds, becoming untargetable and slowing enemies above him by 40% for 1 second.<br /><br />Vladmir deals 20 / 33.75 / 47.5 / 61.25 / 75 (+3.75% of bonus health) magic damage every half second to them and heals himself for 12.5% of the damage done.', '', 'Sanguine Pool', 'Sobafire.com'),
(287, 'vladimir-tides-of-blood.png', '', ' Cooldown: 4.5<br />Cost: 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70<br />Range: 620<br />Vladimir unleashes a torrent of blood dealing 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+45% of ability power) magic damage to nearby enemies.<br /><br />Each cast gives him an Empowered stack (max 4), increasing his healing and regeneration by 8% each. Additionally, his next Tides of Blood deals 25% more damage and costs 50% more Health per stack.', '', 'Tides of Blood', 'Sobafire.com'),
(288, 'vladimir-hemoplague.png', '', ' Cooldown: 150 / 135 / 120<br />Cost: 15<br />Range: 700<br />Vladimir infects the target area with a virulent plague. Affected enemies take 14% increased damage for 5 seconds.<br /><br />After 5 seconds, infected enemies take 150 / 250 / 350 (+70% of ability power) magic damage.', '', 'Hemoplague', 'Sobafire.com'),
(289, 'galio-runic-skin.png', 'Galio Magis Resistance''in %50''sini Ability Power''a çevirir. ', 'Galio receives 50% of his total magic resistance as additional ability power.', 'Runik Deri', 'Runic Skin', 'dağınık'),
(290, 'galio-resolute-smite.png', 'Süre: 7<br>\r\nMaliyet: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90 <br>\r\nMesafe: 900<br>\r\n\r\nGalio gözünden ışın atarak düşmanlara 80 / 135 / 190 / 245 / 300 (+70% of ability power) magic damage vurur. Işının çarptığı düşmanların koşma hızları 2.5 saniye boyunca 24 / 28 / 32 / 36 / 40% oranında düşer.', 'Cooldown: 7<br />Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br />Range: 900<br />Galio fires a concussive blast from his eyes, dealing 80 / 135 / 190 / 245 / 300 (+70% of ability power) magic damage to enemies near the impact location, and reducing their movement speed by 24 / 28 / 32 / 36 / 40% for 2.5 seconds.', 'Azimli Vuruş', 'Resolute Smite', 'dağınık'),
(291, 'galio-bulwark.png', 'Süre: 13<br />Maliyet: 60<br />Mesafe: 800<br />\r\nGalio Takım arkadaşına yada kendisine kalkanını kullanır ve kullanılan kişinin   Armor ve Magic Resistance''ini 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 oranında artırır. Kalkan varken rakipten hasar alınırsa, Galio 25/40/55/70/85 (+0.3). (-20% Arka arkaya atılan her vuruş için) can kazanır Kalkan 4 saniye sürer. ', ' Cooldown: 13<br />Cost: 60<br />Range: 800<br />Galio shields a friendly champion for 4 seconds, increasing their Armor and Magic Resistance by 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90. Each time the unit suffers damage, Galio is healed for 25 / 40 / 55 / 70 / 85 (+30% of ability power) (-20% healing for each consecutive hit).', 'Siper', 'Bulwark', 'dağınık'),
(292, 'galio-righteous-gust.png', 'Süre: 12<br />Maliyet: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90<br />Mesafe: 1000<br />\r\nGalio kanatlarını çarparak fırtına oluşturur ve oluşan fırtına her rakip için 60/105/150/195/240 (+0.5) magic damage vurur. Dost karakterler oluşan rüzgarı takip ederse 5 saniyeliğine 20/28/36/44/52% oranında hız kazanırlar.', ' Cooldown: 12<br />Cost: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90<br />Range: 1000<br />Galio unleashes a gust of concussive wind that deals 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 (+50% of ability power) magic damage to all enemies in its path. A directional draft remains for 5 seconds, increasing the movement speed of allies passing through it by 20 / 28 / 36 / 44 / 52%.', 'Erdemli Fırtına', 'Righteous Gust', 'dağınık'),
(293, 'galio-idol-of-durand.png', 'Süre: 170 / 150 / 130<br />Maliyet: 100 / 150 / 200<br />Mesafe: 550<br />\r\nGalio 2 saniye boyunca güç toplar. Bu esnada etrafındaki rakipler ona vurur. (Galio gelen hasarın %50sini bloklar.)<br><br>\r\n2 saniye sonrasında Galio kendisine saldıran tüm karakterlere 220/330/440 (+0.6) büyü hasarı verir.', ' Cooldown: 170 / 150 / 130<br />Cost: 100 / 150 / 200<br />Range: 550<br />Galio channels for 2 seconds, taunting nearby foes and reducing 50% of incoming damage.<br /><br />After channeling, Galio deals 220 / 330 / 440 (+60% of ability power) magic damage to surrounding enemies, plus an additional 5% damage for each attack suffered while channeling. Maximum +40% bonus damage.', 'Durand''ın İdolü', 'Idol of Durand', 'dağınık'),
(294, 'urgot-zaun-touched-bolt-augmenter.png', '', ' Urgot&acute;s attacks reduce all damage that his target deals by 15% for 2.5 seconds.', '', 'Zaun-Touched Bolt Augmenter', 'Sobafire.com'),
(295, 'urgot-acid-hunter.png', '', ' Cooldown: 2<br />Cost: 40<br />Range: 1000<br />Urgot fires a missile towards the cursor dealing 10 / 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 (+0.85 per Attack Damage) physical damage and applying his passive (does not apply other on-hit effects). Missile-lock can be achieved by holding the cursor over target afflicted by Noxian Corrosive Charge. It won&acute;t lock on invisible minions or wards.', '', 'Acid Hunter', 'Sobafire.com'),
(296, 'urgot-terror-capacitor.png', '', ' Cooldown: 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12<br />Cost: 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 / 75<br /><br />Urgot charges up his terror capacitor to gain a shield that absorbs 80 / 140 / 200 / 260 / 320 (+80% of ability power) damage for 7 seconds. While the shield is active, Urgot&acute;s attacks and missiles slow targets by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40%.', '', 'Terror Capacitor', 'Sobafire.com'),
(297, 'urgot-noxian-corrosive-charge.png', '', ' Cooldown: 11<br />Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70<br />Range: 950<br />(Active): Urgot launches a corrosive charge at a target location. Enemies afflicted by the charge have 12 / 14 / 16 / 18 / 20% reduced armor and take 75 / 130 / 185 / 240 / 295 (+0.6 per bonus AD) physical damage over 5 seconds.<br />Acid Hunter is able to missile-lock onto targets affected by Noxian Corrosive Charge.', '', 'Noxian Corrosive Charge', 'Sobafire.com'),
(298, 'urgot-hyper-kinetic-position-reverse.png', '', ' Urgot charges up his Hyper-Kinetic Position Reverser, gaining 80 / 105 / 130 armor and magic resistance for 5 seconds. The target is stunned for 1 second before swapping positions with Urgot. After the swap, the target is slowed by 40% for 3 seconds.', '', 'Hyper-Kinetic Position Reverse', 'Sobafire.com'),
(299, 'miss-fortune-strut.png', '', ' Miss Fortune gains an additional 25 (+4 each second) movement speed after 7 seconds of not being attacked, increasing each second up to 70 maximum bonus speed.', '', 'Strut', 'Sobafire.com'),
(300, 'miss-fortune-double-up.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5<br />Cost: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90<br />Range: 625<br />(Active): Miss Fortune fires a shot at an enemy target, dealing 25 / 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 (+0.75 per attack damage) physical damage and 115% of that damage to another enemy target behind the first. Both hits apply on-hit effects.<br /><br />* Bounce hit range: 500', '', 'Double Up', 'Sobafire.com'),
(301, 'miss-fortune-impure-shots.png', '', ' Cooldown: 16<br />Cost: 50<br /><br />Passive: Miss Fortune deals 6 / 8 / 10 / 12 / 14 (+5% of ability power) magic damage to her target with each attack, cumulatively stacking up to 4 times on the same target.<br /><br />Active: Miss Fortune&acute;s attack speed is increased by 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% for 6 seconds and causes her attacks to lower healing received and health regeneration by the target by 50% for 3 seconds.', '', 'Impure Shots', 'Sobafire.com'),
(302, 'miss-fortune-make-it-rain.png', '', ' Cooldown: 15<br />Cost: 80 / 85 / 90 / 95 / 100<br />Range: 800<br />Miss Fortune fires hundreds of bullets into the air which rain down at a location after 0.5 seconds, dealing 90 / 145 / 195 / 255 / 310 (+80% of ability power) magic damage over 2 seconds and slowing enemies hit by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 1 second.', '', 'Make it Rain', 'Sobafire.com'),
(303, 'miss-fortune-bullet-time.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120 / 110 / 100<br />Cost: 150<br />Range: 1400<br />Miss Fortune channels a barrage of bullets into a cone in front of her for 2 seconds, dealing 60 / 85 / 110 (+20% of ability power) (+45% of bonus attack damage) magic damage per bullet. There are 6 bullets per wave and 8 waves total. ', '', 'Bullet Time', 'Sobafire.com'),
(304, 'sona-power-chord.png', '', ' After casting 3 spells, Sona&acute;s next attack deals extra 14 + (9 x level) magic damage. This enhanced attack has an additional effect depending on which spell was cast last. <br /><br />Additionally, Sona&acute;s auras persist for 2 seconds after deactivating. Sona&acute;s basic abilities also set off a 2 second cooldown to the other two basic abilties. ', '', 'Power Chord', 'Sobafire.com'),
(305, 'sona-hymn-of-valor.png', '', ' Cooldown: 7<br />Cost: 65<br />Range: 700<br />Sona plays the Hymn of Valor, granting nearby allied champions 8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20 bonus Damage and Ability Power. Additionally, casting this ability sends out bolts of sound, dealing 50 / 100 / 150 / 200 / 250 (+70% of ability power) magic damage to the nearest two enemy champions or monsters.<br /><br />If this spell was last cast when Sona&acute;s Power Chord is ready, her next attack will do double the damage of her Power Chord. ', '', 'Hymn of Valor', 'Sobafire.com'),
(306, 'sona-aria-of-perseverance.png', '', ' Cooldown: 7<br />Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br />Range: 1000<br />Sona plays the Aria of Perseverance, granting nearby allied champions 7 / 9 / 11 / 13 / 15 bonus Armor and Magic Resist. Casting this ability sends out healing melodies, healing Sona and a nearby wounded ally for 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 (+25% of ability power).Additionally, both Sona and the healed champion will have the bonuses of this aura doubled for 3 seconds. <br /><br />If this spell was last cast when Sona&acute;s Power Chord is ready, her next attack will de-buff the target to deal 20% less damage for 4 seconds. ', '', 'Aria of Perseverance', 'Sobafire.com'),
(307, 'sona-song-of-celerity.png', '', ' Cooldown: 7<br />Cost: 65<br />Range: 850<br />Sona plays the Song of Celerity, granting nearby allied champions 8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20 bonus Movement Speed. Additionally, casting this ability energizes nearby allies 6 / 8 / 10 / 12 / 14% additional movement speed for 1.5 seconds.<br /><br />If this spell was last cast when Sona&acute;s Power Chord is ready, her next attack will slow the target by 25% for 2 seconds. ', '', 'Song of Celerity', 'Sobafire.com'),
