(310, 'swain-decrepify.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8<br />Cost: 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100<br />Range: 550<br />Swain sets his raven to cripple an enemy. Over the next three seconds, the target takes 25 / 40 / 55 / 70 / 85 (+30% of ability power) damage per second over time and is slowed by 20 / 23 / 26 / 29 / 32%.', '', 'Decrepify', 'Sobafire.com'),
