(312, 'swain-torment.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 / 85<br />Range: 625<br />Swain afflicts his target, dealing 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235 (+80% of ability power) damage to them over time and causing them to take 8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20%increased damage from Swain&acute;s attacks for 4 seconds. Damage increase applies to summoner spells and items used by Swain.', '', 'Torment', 'Sobafire.com'),
(313, 'swain-ravenous-flock.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 25<br />Range: 700<br />(Toggle): Swain transforms into the form of a raven. During this time, up to 3 lesser ravens strike out at nearby enemies each second, one raven per enemy, dealing 60 / 75 / 90 (+20% of ability power) magic damage. Swain is healed for 75% the damage dealt to champions and by 25% of the damage dealt to minions and monsters. The cost to sustain Ravenous Flock increases by 5 / 7 / 9 mana every second. ', '', 'Ravenous Flock', 'Sobafire.com'),
