(315, 'lux-light-binding.png', '', ' Cooldown: 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11<br />Cost: 60 / 75 / 90 / 105 / 120<br />Range: 1000<br />Lux releases a sphere of light that immobilizes and deals 60 / 110 / 160 / 210 / 260 (+70% of ability power)magic damage to up to two enemy units for 2 seconds, dealing 50% effect and damage to the 2nd unit struck.', '', 'Light Binding', 'Sobafire.com'),
