(317, 'lux-lucent-singularity.png', '', ' Cooldown: 11<br />Cost: 70 / 85 / 100 / 115 / 130<br />Range: 1100<br />Fires an anomaly of twisted light to an area, which slows nearby enemies by 20 / 24 / 28 / 32 / 36%. Zone lasts 5 seconds. Lux can detonate it to deal 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 (+60% of ability power) magic damage to enemies in the area of effect.', '', 'Lucent Singularity', 'Sobafire.com'),
(318, 'lux-finales-funkeln.png', '', ' Cooldown: 80 / 60 / 40<br />Cost: 100 / 150 / 200<br />Range: 3000<br />After gathering energy, Lux fires a beam of light that deals 300 / 400 / 500 (+75% of ability power) damage to all targets in the area. It ignites and refreshes Lux&acute;s Illumination debuff if it hits enemies already afflicted.', '', 'Finales Funkeln', 'Sobafire.com'),
(319, 'leblanc-mirror-image.png', '', ' When LeBlanc is brought below 40% health, she instantly becomes stealthed for half a second. When the stealth fades, she creates a Mirror Image that deals no damage and lasts for up to 8 seconds. This can only occur once per minute.', '', 'Mirror Image', 'Sobafire.com'),
(320, 'leblanc-sigil-of-silence.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6<br />Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br />Range: 700<br />LeBlanc projects an orb towards her target, dealing 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 (+60% of ability power) magic damage and marking the target for 3.5 seconds. If the target takes damage from one of Leblanc&acute;s abilities, the mark will trigger, dealing 20 / 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 (+30% of ability power) magic damage and silencing the target for 2 seconds.', '', 'Sigil of Silence', 'Sobafire.com'),
(321, 'leblanc-distortion.png', '', ' Cooldown: 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12<br />Cost: 80 / 90 / 100 / 110 / 120<br />Range: 600<br />LeBlanc rapidly moves to a target location, dealing 85 / 125 / 165 / 205 / 245 (+60% of ability power) magic damage to nearby units. In the following 3 seconds, she can activate Distortion again to return to her starting location.', '', 'Distortion', 'Sobafire.com'),
(322, 'leblanc-ethereal-chains.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 80<br />Range: 950<br />LeBlanc flings illusionary chains towards a target location. If it hits an enemy unit, it will deal 40 / 65 / 90 / 115 / 140 (+50% of ability power) initial magic damage and slow their movement speed by 25%. If the target remains shackled for (1/1.3/1.6/1.9/2.2) seconds, the target takes additional 40 / 65 / 90 / 115 / 140 (+50% of ability power) magic damage and is unable to move.', '', 'Ethereal Chains', 'Sobafire.com'),
(323, 'leblanc-mimic.png', '', ' Cooldown: 40 / 32 / 24<br />Cost: 100 / 50 / 1<br /><br />LeBlanc can cast the previous spell she cast. The mimicked spell deals 10% / 25% / 40% increased damage.', '', 'Mimic', 'Sobafire.com'),
(324, 'irelia-ionian-fervor.png', '', ' Range: 800<br />Reduces the duration of stuns, slows, taunts, fears, snares, and immobilizes for each nearby enemy champion.<br />1 Champion: 10%<br />2 Champions: 25%<br />3 Champions: 40%', '', 'Ionian Fervor', 'Sobafire.com'),
(325, 'irelia-bladesurge.png', '', ' Cooldown: 14 / 12 / 10 / 8 / 6<br />Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br />Range: 650<br />Irelia dashes forward to strike her target for 20 / 50 / 80 / 110 / 140 (+1 per Attack Damage) physical damage. This applies on-hit effects. If it kills the target, Bladesurge&acute;s cooldown refreshes and refunds 35 Mana.', '', 'Bladesurge', 'Sobafire.com'),
(326, 'irelia-hiten-style.png', '', ' Cooldown: 15<br />Cost: 40<br /><br />Irelia is skilled in the art of Hiten, passively giving her physical attacks 10 / 14 / 18 / 22 / 26 health restoration. Activating Hiten Style adds 15 / 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 true damage to her physical attacks for 6 seconds.', '', 'Hiten Style', 'Sobafire.com'),
(327, 'irelia-equilibrium-strike.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8<br />Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70<br />Range: 425<br />Irelia&acute;s attack balances the scales, dealing 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280 (+50% of ability power) damage and slowing the target by 60% for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds. However, if the target has a higher Health % than Irelia, then the blow stuns the target for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds instead.', '', 'Equilibrium Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(328, 'irelia-transcendent-blades.png', '', ' Cooldown: 60 / 50 / 40<br />Cost: 100<br />Range: 1200<br />Irelia summons 4 spirit blades which she can fling at her enemies. These blades deal 80 / 120 / 160 (+0.6 per bonus Attack Damage AND +0.5 per bonus Ability Power) physical damage to enemies that they pass through, and she heals for 25% of that damage vs champions and 10% vs minions.', '', 'Transcendent Blades', 'Sobafire.com'),
