(330, 'trundle-rabid-bite.png', '', ' Cooldown: 4<br />Cost: 40<br /><br />Trundle bites his opponent instead of attacking for his next standard attack, dealing 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 + 80% / 90% / 100% / 110% / 120% of his attack damage as physical damage.<br /><br />This attack increases Trundle&acute;s attack damage by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 for 8 seconds, with his opponent losing half of this amount.', '', 'Rabid Bite', 'Sobafire.com'),
(331, 'trundle-contaminate.png', '', ' Cooldown: 15<br />Cost: 60<br />Range: 900<br />Trundle infects a target location with his curse for 8 seconds, gaining 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60% attack speed, 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% movement speed, and 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% crowd control reduction while on it. ', '', 'Contaminate', 'Sobafire.com'),
(332, 'trundle-pillar-of-filth.png', '', ' Cooldown: 23 / 20 / 17 / 14 / 11<br />Cost: 60<br />Range: 1000<br />Trundle creates a plagued beacon at a target location for 6.5 seconds, which becomes impassable terrain and slows all nearby enemy units by 25% / 30% / 35% / 40% / 45% while they are in the vicinity and for 1.25 seconds after.', '', 'Pillar of Filth', 'Sobafire.com'),
(333, 'trundle-agony.png', '', ' Cooldown: 80 / 70 / 60<br />Cost: 75<br />Range: 700<br />Trundle immediately steals 100 / 175 / 250 (+60% of ability power) of his target&acute;s health (magic damage) and 15 / 20 / 25% of their armor and magic resistance. Over the next six seconds the amount of health, armor, and magic resistance stolen is doubled.', '', 'Agony', 'Sobafire.com'),
(334, 'cassiopeia-deadly-cadence.png', '', ' After casting a spell, any subsequent spellcasts will cost 10% less for 5 seconds. This ability stacks up to 5 times.', '', 'Deadly Cadence', 'Sobafire.com'),
(335, 'cassiopeia-noxious-blast.png', '', ' Cooldown: 3<br />Cost: 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 / 75<br />Range: 850<br />Cassiopeia blasts an area with a delayed high damaging poison, dealing 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235 (+90% of ability power) magic damage over 3 seconds and granting her 15% / 17.5% / 20% / 22.5% / 25% movement speed for 3 seconds if she hits a champion.', '', 'Noxious Blast', 'Sobafire.com'),
(336, 'cassiopeia-miasma.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9<br />Cost: 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110<br />Range: 850<br />Cassiopeia releases a growing cloud of poison that lasts for 7 seconds, giving vision of the area. Any enemy that passes through it is poisoned for 2 seconds, dealing 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 (+15% of ability power) magic damage each second and slowing them for 15% / 20% / 25% / 30% / 35%. Continual exposure renews this poison.', '', 'Miasma', 'Sobafire.com'),
(337, 'cassiopeia-twin-fang.png', '', ' Cooldown: 5<br />Cost: 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90<br />Range: 700<br />Cassiopeia deals 60/95/130/165/200 (+55% of ability power) magic damage to her target. If the target is poisoned then Twin Fang&acute;s cooldown is reduced to 0.5 seconds.', '', 'Twin Fang', 'Sobafire.com'),
(338, 'cassiopeia-petrifying-gaze.png', '', ' Cooldown: 130 / 120 / 110<br />Cost: 120 / 160 / 200<br />Range: 850<br />(Active): Cassiopeia deals 200 / 325 / 450 (+60% of ability power)magic damage to all enemies in front of her. Enemies facing her are stunned for 2 seconds, while enemies facing away are slowed by 60% for the same duration.', '', 'Petrifying Gaze', 'Sobafire.com'),
(339, 'caitlyn-headshot.png', '', ' Every 8 / 7 / 6 attacks (attacks while in brush count as 2), Caitlyn will fire a headshot, dealing either 150% damage to a champion or 250% damage to a minion.', '', 'Headshot', 'Sobafire.com'),
(340, 'caitlyn-piltover-peacemaker.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6<br />Cost: 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90<br /><br />Caitlyn revs up her rifle for 1 second to unleash a penetrating shot which deals 20 / 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 (+1.3 per attack damage) physical damage to targets in a line. It deals 15% less damage to subsequent targets, down to a minimum of 40%. ', '', 'Piltover Peacemaker', 'Sobafire.com'),
(341, 'caitlyn-yordle-snap-trap.png', '', ' Cooldown: 20 / 17 / 14 / 11 / 8<br />Cost: 50<br />Range: 800<br />Caitlyn sets up to three traps which trigger on champions. When sprung, the trap immobilizes the champion, deals 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280 (+60% of ability power) magic damage over 1.5 seconds and reveals the target for 9 seconds. Traps last 4 minutes.', '', 'Yordle Snap Trap', 'Sobafire.com'),
