(343, 'caitlyn-ace-in-the-hole.png', '', ' Cooldown: 90 / 75 / 60<br />Cost: 100<br />Range: 1900 / 2050 / 2200<br />Caitlyn takes time to line up the perfect shot, dealing 250 / 475 / 700 (+2.0 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to a single target at a huge range. Enemy champions can intercept the bullet for their ally. It provides vision of the target for the duration. ', '', 'Ace in the Hole', 'Sobafire.com'),
(344, 'renekton-reign-of-anger.png', '', ' Renekton gains 5 Fury per autoattack. Having sufficient fury empowers Renekton&acute;s abilities with bonus effects, but this drains Fury. When out of combat for 12 seconds, Renekton loses 5 Fury per 2 seconds.<br /><br />When Renekton is below 50% life he generates 50% more fury.', '', 'Reign of Anger', 'Sobafire.com'),
(345, 'renekton-cull-the-meek.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8<br />Range: 450<br />Renekton swings his blade dealing 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+0.8 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to nearby enemies and healing for 5% of the damage dealt up to a hard cap of 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150 HP. Each target hit grants 5 Fury, up to 25. Heal amount is quadrupled against champions.<br /><br />When Renekton has more than 50 Fury he deals 90 / 135 / 180 / 225 / 270 (+1.2 per bonus attack damage) and healing for 10% of the damage dealt up to a hard cap of 150 / 225 / 300 / 375 / 450 HP.Heal amount is quadrupled against champions. Consumes 50 Fury. ', '', 'Cull the Meek', 'Sobafire.com'),
