(347, 'renekton-slice-and-dice.png', '', ' Cooldown: 18 / 17 / 16 / 15 / 14<br />Range: 550<br />Slice: Renekton dashes forward, dealing 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 (+0.9 per bonus attack damage) damage to targets along the way. If he hits a target he gains the ability to use Dice for 4 seconds.<br /><br />Dice: Renekton dashes, dealing 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 (+0.9 per bonus attack damage) damage along the way. When Renekton has more than 50 Fury during Dice, he deals 45 / 90 / 135 / 180 / 225 (+1.35 per bonus attack damage) additional damage and shreds the armor of targets he hits by 15 / 17.5 / 20 / 22.5 / 25% for 4 seconds. Consumes 50 Fury.', '', 'Slice and Dice', 'Sobafire.com'),
(348, 'renekton-dominus.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120<br />Range: 20<br />Renekton empowers himself with dark energies, gaining increased size and 300 / 450 / 600 health for 15 seconds. While empowered, he deals 40 / 70 / 100 (+10% of ability power) magic damage to nearby enemies and generates 5 Fury per second.', '', 'Dominus', 'Sobafire.com'),
(349, 'karma-inner-flame.png', '', ' Karma gains (30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 140) increased ability power corresponding to her % of missing Health.', '', 'Inner Flame', 'Sobafire.com'),
(350, 'karma-heavenly-wave.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6<br />Cost: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90<br />Range: 700<br />Karma sends forth a wave of hidden blades from her fans, dealing (70 /110/150/190/230/270) (+60% of ability power) magic damage to units in a cone in front of her.<br /><br />Mantra Bonus: In addition to dealing damage to enemies, Heavenly Wave will also heal Karma and her allies in the cone for (35/55/75/95/115/135). An additional 5% (+1% per 50 ability power) of health the targets are missing is added to the heal. <br /><br />Rank 6 Cost: 95 Mana', '', 'Heavenly Wave', 'Sobafire.com'),
(351, 'karma-spirit-bond.png', '', ' Cooldown: 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11<br />Cost: 65 / 75 / 85 / 95 / 105<br />Range: 800<br />Karma creates a beam between an ally or enemy for up to 5 seconds. Allied anchors move (10/12/14/16/18/20%) faster and enemy anchors are slowed for the same amount. The beam deals (80/125/170/215/260/305) (+70% of ability power) magic damage to enemies and applies the same movement speed adjustment anchors receive to any champion it passes through for 3 seconds. The beam breaks if the bonded target is stealthed.<br /><br />Mantra Bonus: Karma strengthens the bond to double the effect of the movement speed modifier. <br /><br />Rank 6 Cooldown: 10 seconds<br />Rank 6 Cost: 115 mana', '', 'Spirit Bond', 'Sobafire.com'),
(352, 'karma-soul-shield.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110<br />Range: 650<br />Karma summons a protective shield on an ally or herself that absorbs (80/120/160/200/240/280) (+80% of ability power) damage for 5 seconds.<br /><br />Mantra Bonus: In addition to casting the shield, a surge of energy bursts out from the shield dealing (80 /120/160/200/240/280) 0.8) magic damage to enemy units around her target. <br /><br />Rank 6 Cost: 120 mana', '', 'Soul Shield', 'Sobafire.com'),
(353, 'karma-mantra.png', '', ' Cooldown: 0.25<br /><br />Karma empowers her next ability to do an additional effect. Karma gains a charge every (30/25/20) seconds and stores up to 2 charges. The refresh rate is reduced by cooldown reduction and does not progress when having max charges. <br /><br />Mantra is available from level 1 and does not require skill points. The time needed to load a charge is reduced at level 7 and 13. ', '', 'Mantra', 'Sobafire.com'),
(354, 'maokai-sap-magic.png', '', ' Each time a champion near Maokai casts a spell, he gains a charge of Magical Sap. When he has 5 charges, his next melee attack drains energy from his target, healing Maokai for 7% of his maximum health.', '', 'Sap Magic', 'Sobafire.com'),
(355, 'maokai-arcane-smash.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6<br />Cost: 55<br />Range: 700<br />Maokai slams the ground, the force of which knocks nearby enemies back and sends an arcane shockwave forward, dealing 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+40% of ability power) magic damage and slowing his enemies by 20 / 27 / 34 / 41 / 48 % for 2 seconds. Enemies close to Maokai are knocked up briefly.', '', 'Arcane Smash', 'Sobafire.com'),
(356, 'maokai-twisted-advance.png', '', ' Cooldown: 13<br />Cost: 75 / 80 / 85 / 90 / 95<br />Range: 650<br />Maokai transforms into a cloud of arcane energy, quickly traveling to a target enemy. The target takes 80 / 115 / 150 / 185 / 220 (+80% of ability power) magic damage and is rooted in place for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds.', '', 'Twisted Advance', 'Sobafire.com'),
(357, 'maokai-sapling-toss.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12<br />Cost: 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110<br />Range: 1100<br />Maokai hurls a sapling to a target area, dealing 40 / 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 (+40% of ability power) magic damage on impact. The sapling becomes implanted in the ground, warding a nearby area for up to 35 seconds. After a 1 second delay after landing, the sapling will seek out nearby enemies. When an enemy approaches, the sapling will chase for up to 2.5 seconds and explode in an arcane blast that deals 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280 (+60% of ability power) magic damage to enemies.', '', 'Sapling Toss', 'Sobafire.com'),
(358, 'maokai-vengeful-maelstrom.png', '', ' Cooldown: 40 / 30 / 20<br />Cost: 75<br />Range: 575<br />Maokai shields his allies by drawing power from hostile spells and attacks, reducing non-tower damage done to allied champions in the area by 20%. Maokai can prolong the effect as long as he has mana to spend on it (Upkeep Cost: 30 mana per second). When the effect ends, Maokai unleashes the absorbed energy to deal 100 / 150 / 200 (+50% of ability power) (+2 bonus damage per damage absorbed) damage to enemies within the vortex. Maximum 200 / 250 / 300 bonus damage.', '', 'Vengeful Maelstrom', 'Sobafire.com'),
(359, 'jarvan-iv-martial-cadence.png', '', ' Jarvan IV&acute;s first attack on his target deals 8% of the target&acute;s current health as bonus magic damage, this caps at 400 damage. This effect cannot occur on the same target for 6 seconds. ', '', 'Martial Cadence', 'Sobafire.com'),
(360, 'jarvan-iv-dragon-strike.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6<br />Cost: 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65<br />Range: 770<br />Jarvan IV extends his lance through his opponent, dealing 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+1.1 per bonus attack damage) physical damage and lowering their armor by 10 / 14 / 18 / 22 / 26% for 3 seconds. If its lance contacts his standard it will pull Jarvan IV to its location, knocking up all enemies in his path. ', '', 'Dragon Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(361, 'jarvan-iv-golden-aegis.png', '', ' Cooldown: 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12<br />Cost: 75<br /><br />Jarvan IV forges a shield protecting him for 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210 (+20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 per nearby enemy champion) damage for 5 seconds and slowing surrounding enemies by 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35% for 2 seconds upon activation. The shield adds more mitigation for every enemy champion nearby when activating. ', '', 'Golden Aegis', 'Sobafire.com'),
(362, 'jarvan-iv-demacian-standard.png', '', ' Cooldown: 13<br />Cost: 60<br />Range: 830<br />Passive: Grants Jarvan a bonus 10 / 13 / 16 / 19 / 22% attack speed and 10 / 13 / 16 / 19 / 22 armor.<br /><br />Active: Jarvan IV throws a Demacian flag to a nearby area, dealing 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 (+80% of ability power) magic damage to enemies in the area and granting his passive benefits to nearby allies and again to himself for 8 seconds.', '', 'Demacian Standard', 'Sobafire.com'),
(363, 'jarvan-iv-cataclysm.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120 / 105 / 90<br />Cost: 100 / 125 / 150<br />Range: 650<br />Jarvan IV heroically leaps to an enemy champion, dealing 200 / 325 / 450 (+1.5 per bonus attack damage) physical damage and creating a circle of impassable terrain around them for a 3.5 second duration. Jarvan IV can destroy the area by activating it again. Champions can still leave or enter the area by using teleport abilities. ', '', 'Cataclysm', 'Sobafire.com'),
(364, 'nocturne-umbra-blades.png', 'Her 10 saniyede bir Nocturne’un saldırısı etrafındaki düşmanlara %120 oranında fiziksel hasar verir ve vurduğu hedef başına kendisini 15/20/25 değerlerinde can doldurur. Nocturne’nun her normal saldırısı bu yeteneğinin zamanlamasını 1 saniye düşürür.', 'Every 10 seconds, Nocturne&acute;s next attack strikes surrounding enemies for 120% of his physical damage and heals himself for 15 / 20 / 25 per target hit. Nocturne&acute;s basic attacks reduce this cooldown by 1 second.', 'Umbra Blades', 'Umbra Blades', 'GriSayfalar'),
(365, 'nocturne-duskbringer.png', 'Nocturne 60/105/150/195/240 (+her ekstra attack damage başına 0.75) oranında hasar veren bir hayalet kılıç fırlatır. Fırlattığı bu kılıç 5 saniyeliğine Alacakaranlık İz’i yaratır.\r\n<br><br>\r\nNocturne bu izin üzerindeyken birim çarpışmalarını es geçer ve %15/20/25/30/35 oranında hareket hızı ve 15/25/35/45/55 değerinde Attack Damage (Saldırı Hasarı) kazanır.', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br />Range: 1200<br />Nocturne throws a shadow blade which deals physical damage 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 (+0.75 per bonus attack damage), leaves a Dusk Trail, and causes champions who are hit to also leave a Dusk Trail for 5 seconds. While on the trail, Nocturne ignores unit collision and has increased Movement Speed 15% / 20% / 25% / 30% / 35% and Attack Damage 15 / 25 / 35 / 45 / 55.', 'Duskbringer', 'Duskbringer', 'GriSayfalar'),
(366, 'nocturne-shroud-of-darkness.png', 'Nocturne 2 saniyeliğine sihirsel bir bariyer oluşturur ve bir sonraki düşman yeteneğini engeller. Eğer bir yetenek bu kalkan ile engellenirse, Nocturne’un pasif olarak kazandığı saldırı hızı 5 saniyeliğine ikiye katlanır.<br><br>\r\nPasif: Nocturne %20/25/30/35/40 oranında Attack Speed (Saldırı Hızı) kazanır.', ' Cooldown: 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12<br />Cost: 50<br /><br />Nocturne empowers his blades, passively gaining attack speed 20% / 25% / 30% / 35% / 40%. Activating Shroud of Darkness allows Nocturne to fade into the shadows, creating a magical barrier for 2 seconds which blocks a single enemy ability and doubles his passive attack speed for 5 seconds if successful.', 'Shroud of Darkness', 'Shroud of Darkness', 'GriSayfalar'),
(367, 'nocturne-unspeakable-horror.png', 'Nocturne hedefinin zihnine bir kabus yerleştirir ve iki saniye içerisinde 50/100/150/200/250 (+%100 Ability Power) oranında büyü hasarı verir (magic damage). Eğer 2 saniyenin tamamında hedef mesafenin içerisinde kalabilirse hedef 1/1.25/1.5/1.75/2 saniyeliğine korkar (fear etkisi).', ' Cooldown: 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11<br />Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br />Range: 425<br />Nocturne plants a nightmare into his target&acute;s mind, dealing damage each second for total 50 / 100 / 150 / 200 / 250 (+100% of ability power) over 2 seconds and fearing the target for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds if they do not get out of (465) range by the end of the duration.', 'Unspeakable Horror', 'Unspeakable Horror', 'GriSayfalar'),
(368, 'nocturne-paranoia.png', 'Nocturne 4 saniyeliğine tüm düşmanların görüş açılarını yok eder, düşmanlar kendileri dışında bir şey göremezler. Paranoia aktifken Nocturne 2000/2750/3500 mesafesinde yer alan bir düşmana anında saldırı gerçekleştirebilir ve 150/250/350 (her bonus attack damage başına +1.2) fiziksel hasar verir.', ' Cooldown: 160 / 130 / 100<br />Cost: 100<br />Range: 2500 / 3250 / 4000<br />Nocturne reduces the sight radius of all enemy champions and removes their ally vision for 4 seconds, this includes champions, minions, wards and towers. He can then launch himself at a enemy champion with a large range 2500 / 3250 / 4000. Deals 150 / 300 / 450 (+1.2 per bonus attack damage) physical damage on arrival.', 'Paranoia', 'Paranoia', 'GriSayfalar'),
(369, 'lee-sin-flurry.png', '', ' After Lee Sin uses an ability, his next 2 basic attacks within 3 seconds gain 50% Attack Speed and return 15 energy each.', '', 'Flurry', 'Sobafire.com'),
(370, 'lee-sin-sonic-wave-resonating-strike.png', '', ' Cooldown: 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7<br />Cost: 50<br />Range: 975<br />Sonic Wave: Lee Sin projects a discordant wave of sound to locate his enemies, dealing 50 / 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 (+90% per bonus attack damage) physical damage to the first enemy it encounters and revealing them for 3 seconds. If Sonic Wave hits, Lee Sin can cast Resonating Strike within the next 3 seconds.<br /><br />Resonating Strike (30 energy): Lee Sin dashes to the enemy hit by Sonic Wave, dealing 50 / 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 (+90% per bonus attack damage) physical damage plus 10% of their missing health as physical damage.', '', 'Sonic Wave / Resonating Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(371, 'lee-sin-safeguard-iron-will.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8<br />Cost: 50<br />Range: 700<br />Safeguard: Lee Sin rushes towards a target ally, shielding them both for (40/80/120/160/200) (+80% of ability power) for the next 5 seconds. After using Safeguard, Lee Sin can cast Iron Will for the next 3 seconds.<br /><br />Iron Will (30 energy): Lee Sin&acute;s intense training allows him to thrive in battle. For 5 seconds, Lee Sin gains 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 % lifesteal and spell vamp. He also gains 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 armor.', '', 'Safeguard / Iron Will', 'Sobafire.com'),
(372, 'lee-sin-tempest-cripple.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 50<br />Range: 350<br />Tempest: Lee Sin smashes the ground sending out a shockwave that deals 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 (+100% per bonus attack damage) magic damage and reveals enemy units hit for 4 seconds. If Tempest hits an enemy, Lee Sin can cast cripple for the next 3 seconds.<br /><br />Cripple (30 energy): Lee Sin cripples nearby enemies revealed by Tempest, reducing their Movement and Attack Speed by 30 / 37.5 / 45 / 52.5 / 60 % for 4 seconds. Movement and Attack Speed recover gradually over the duration.', '', 'Tempest / Cripple', 'Sobafire.com'),
(373, 'lee-sin-dragons-rage.png', '', ' Cooldown: 90 / 75 / 60<br />Range: 375<br />Lee Sin performs a powerful roundhouse kick launching his target back 1200 units, dealing 200 / 400 / 600 (+200% per bonus attack damage) physical damage to the target and any enemies they collide with. Enemies the target collides with are knocked into the air for a short duration.', '', 'Dragon&acute;s Rage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(374, 'brand-blaze.png', '', ' Brand&acute;s spells light his targets ablaze, dealing 2% of their maximum Health in magic damage per second for 4 seconds.', '', 'Blaze', 'Sobafire.com'),
(375, 'brand-sear.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8 / 7.5 / 7 / 6.5 / 6<br />Cost: 50<br />Range: 900<br />Brand launches a ball of fire forward that deals 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 (+65% of ability power) magic damage. If the target is ablaze, the target will be stunned for 2 seconds.', '', 'Sear', 'Sobafire.com'),
(376, 'brand-pillar-of-flame.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110<br />Range: 900<br />After a short delay, Brand creates a pillar of flame at a target area, dealing 75 / 120 / 165 / 210 / 255 (+60% of ability power) magic damage to enemy units with the area. Units that are ablaze take an additional 25% damage.', '', 'Pillar of Flame', 'Sobafire.com'),
(377, 'brand-conflagration.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8<br />Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br />Range: 625<br />Brand conjures a powerful blast at his target, dealing 70 / 105 / 140 / 175 / 210 (+55% of ability power) magic damage to them. If the target is ablaze the conflagration will damage nearby enemies as well.', '', 'Conflagration', 'Sobafire.com'),
(378, 'brand-pyroclasm.png', '', ' Cooldown: 105 / 90 / 75<br />Cost: 100 / 150 / 200<br />Range: 750<br />Brand unleashes a devastating torrent of fire that bounces between enemies, dealing 150 / 250 / 350 (+50% of ability power) magic damage each time it bounces. If a target is ablaze, Pyroclasm&acute;s missile speed increases. It will bounce five times, and can hit the same enemy up to three times.', '', 'Pyroclasm', 'Sobafire.com'),
(379, 'rumble-junkyard-titan.png', '', ' Rumble&acute;s abilities don&acute;t cost anything but generate 20 heat. When Rumble reaches 50 heat, he is in the "Danger Zone", causing all his basic spells to have additional effects. When Rumble reaches 100 heat he overheats, silencing himself for 6 seconds to cooldown completely and causing his physical attacks to deal an additional 20 + (5 x level) + (0.35 per ability power) magic damage for the duration. While not overheated, after 4 seconds of not using his basic abilities he will start losing heat at a rate of 5 every half second, and 2.5 seconds later at a rate of 10 every half second.', '', 'Junkyard Titan', 'Sobafire.com'),
(380, 'rumble-flamespitter.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6<br />Range: 490<br />Rumble begins torching the area in front of him with his flamethrower, dealing 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 (+45% of ability power) magic damage per second to all units in a cone in front of him for 3 seconds. He can move, attack and use other abilities while the flamethrower is on.<br /><br />While in the &quot;Danger Zone&quot;, this spell deals 30% additional damage. ', '', 'Flamespitter', 'Sobafire.com'),
(381, 'rumble-scrap-shield.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6<br /><br />Rumble creates a shield blocking 50 / 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 (+40% of ability power) incoming damage for 2 seconds, in addition Rumble receives a 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30% movement speed boost for 1 second.<br /><br />While in the "Danger Zone", the shield’s strength and movement speed boost are increased by 30%.', '', 'Scrap Shield', 'Sobafire.com'),
(382, 'rumble-electro-harpoon.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br /><br />Rumble shoots a taser that deals 55 / 85 / 115 / 145 / 175 (+50% of ability power) magic damage and applies a 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35% slow on the enemy hit for three seconds. A second shot can be fired for no additional cost within the next three seconds. The slows from these two tasers can stack with themselves and the duration will be refreshed with the second hit.<br /><br />While in the "Danger Zone", the damage and slow percentage are increased by 30%.', '', 'Electro-Harpoon', 'Sobafire.com'),
(383, 'rumble-the-equalizer.png', '', ' Cooldown: 90 / 75 / 60<br /><br />Rumble calls down a line of rockets over the target linear location, it uses click and drag targeting. The rockets deal an initial 150 / 225 / 350 (+50% of ability power) magic damage to all enemies hit on arrival, and also leave a trail of destruction for 5 seconds that slows by 35% and deals 120 / 160 / 200 (+25% of ability power) magic damage per second to all enemies standing on the area.<br /><br />This ability does not generate heat.', '', 'The Equalizer', 'Sobafire.com'),
(384, 'vayne-night-hunter.png', '', ' Range: 2000<br />Vayne ruthlessly hunts evil-doers. She gains 40 Movement Speed when moving towards an enemy champion. ', '', 'Night Hunter', 'Sobafire.com'),
(385, 'vayne-tumble.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6 / 5 / 4 / 3 / 2<br />Cost: 40<br />Range: 250<br />Vayne tumbles, maneuvering to carefully place her next shot. She rolls toward the cursor and her next attack deals 40/45/50/55/60% bonus damage.', '', 'Tumble', 'Sobafire.com'),
(386, 'vayne-silver-bolts.png', '', ' Vayne tips her bolts with a rare metal, toxic to evil things. The third consecutive attack or ability against the same target will deal 20/30/40/50/60 additional damage plus 4/5/6/7/8% of the target&acute;s maximum health as bonus true damage. (Max damage vs. monsters is capped at 200) ', '', 'Silver Bolts', 'Sobafire.com'),
(387, 'vayne-condemn.png', '', ' Cooldown: 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12<br />Cost: 90<br />Range: 575<br />Vayne draws a heavy crossbow from her back, and fires a huge bolt at her target, dealing 45/80/115/150/185(+0.5 per bonus attack damage) physical damage and knocking them back. If they collide with terrain, they are impaled, dealing 45/80/115/150/185(+0.5 per bonus attack damage) bonus damage and stunning them for 1.5 seconds. ', '', 'Condemn', 'Sobafire.com'),
(388, 'vayne-final-hour.png', '', ' Cooldown: 70<br /><br />Readying herself for an epic confrontation, Vayne gains 25/40/55 increased attack damage, 1.5 second stealth during Tumble, and triple the bonus movement speed from Night Hunter lasting 8/10/12 seconds. ', '', 'Final Hour', 'Sobafire.com'),
(389, 'orianna-clockwork-windup.png', '', ' Orianna&acute;s autoattacks deal additional 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 (+20% of ability power) magic damage every hit, subsequent attacks on the same target within a few seconds will add 15% more damage per hit. This bonus stacks up to three times.', '', 'Clockwork Windup', 'Sobafire.com'),
(390, 'orianna-command-attack.png', '', ' Cooldown: 6 / 5.5 / 5 / 4.5 / 4<br />Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70<br />Range: 825<br />Orianna commands her ball to fly towards target location, dealing 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 (+60% of ability power) damage to targets hit but dealing 10% less damage for each additional target hit (minimum 40%). Her ball remains behind at that location afterwards.', '', 'Command: Attack', 'Sobafire.com'),
(391, 'orianna-command-dissonance.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9<br />Cost: 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110<br />Range: 925<br />(Active): Orianna commands her ball to emit a magnetic pulse, dealing 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+60% of ability power) damage to units around it. Afterwards, the ball leaves a field behind for 3 seconds that speeds up allies and slows enemies for 2 seconds for 20/25/30/35/40% movement speed. ', '', 'Command: Dissonance', 'Sobafire.com'),
(392, 'orianna-command-protect.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9<br />Cost: 40<br />Range: 925<br />(Passive): The allied champion the ball is attached to gains 10/15/20/25/30 bonus armor and magic resistance. <br /><br />(Active): Orianna commands her ball to fly to and attach onto an allied champion, dealing60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+45% of ability power) damage to enemies it passes through and shielding the allied champion 4 seconds for 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 (+40% of ability power) when it arrives. ', '', 'Command: Protect', 'Sobafire.com'),
(393, 'orianna-command-shockwave.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120 / 105 / 90<br />Cost: 100 / 125 / 150<br />Range: 925<br />Active): Orianna commands her ball to emit a shockwave after a short delay, flinging affected enemies in the vicinity into the air a set distance towards, and possibly over, her ball. Deals 150 / 225 / 300 (+70% of ability power) damage.', '', 'Command: Shockwave', 'Sobafire.com'),
(394, 'yorick-unholy-covenant.png', '', ' Yorick&acute;s summoned ghouls deal 35% of Yorick’s attack damage and have 35% of his total health. The Ghoul&acute;s health is reduced by 20% of their max health every second. In addition, Yorick takes 5% less damage and his attacks deal 5% more damage for each summon that is active.', '', 'Unholy Covenant', 'Sobafire.com');
INSERT INTO `lol_skills` (`SkillNum`, `imgPath`, `TR`, `EN`, `TR_skillname`, `EN_skillname`, `Cevirmen`) VALUES
(395, 'yorick-omen-of-war.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5<br />Cost: 40<br /><br />Yorick&acute;s next attack will deal 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 (+1.2 per attack damage) bonus physical damage and summon a Spectral Ghoul.<br /><br /><br />The Spectral Ghoul deals 8 / 16 / 24 / 32 / 40 extra physical damage (on top of the 35% of Yorick&acute;s bonus damage) and moves faster than the rest of the ghouls. While the ghoul is active, Yorick moves 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35% faster as well. ', '', 'Omen of War', 'Sobafire.com'),
(396, 'yorick-omen-of-pestilence.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12<br />Cost: 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60<br />Range: 600<br />Yorick summons a Decaying Ghoul that arrives with a violent explosion, dealing 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 (+100% of ability power) magic damage and slowing nearby enemies by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 1.5 seconds. While the Decaying Ghoul remains alive, nearby enemies continue to be slowed by 10 / 12.5 / 15 / 17.5 / 20%. ', '', 'Omen of Pestilence', 'Sobafire.com'),
(397, 'yorick-omen-of-famine.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6<br />Cost: 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 / 75<br />Range: 550<br />Yorick deals 55 / 85 / 115 / 145 / 175 (+1.0 per bonus attack damage) magic damage and heals for 40% of the damage dealt. A Ravenous Ghoul is summoned behind his target, which heals Yorick for the damage it deals.', '', 'Omen of Famine', 'Sobafire.com'),
(398, 'yorick-omen-of-death.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120 / 105 / 90<br />Cost: 100<br />Range: 900<br />Yorick conjures a revenant in the image of one of his allies that will have 50 / 75 / 100% of their max health and 45 / 60 / 75% of their attack damage, which lasts up to 10 seconds. If his ally dies while its revenant is alive, the revenant sacrifices itself to reanimate them temporarily by restoring them to full health and give them time to enact vengeance. The reanimation will last for up to 10 seconds. During this time, the ally can use all of his abilities.', '', 'Omen of Death', 'Sobafire.com'),
(399, 'leona-sunlight.png', '', ' Leona&acute;s damaging spells affect the target with Sunlight for 3.5 seconds. When allied champions deal damage to those targets they consume the Sunlight debuff to deal 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 / 95 / 110 / 125 / 140 additional magic damage. Leona is unable to activate the additional damage herself. ', '', 'Sunlight', 'Sobafire.com'),
(400, 'leona-shield-of-daybreak.png', '', ' Cooldown: 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7<br />Cost: 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65<br /><br />Leona&acute;s next basic attack will deal 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 (+30% of ability power) additional magic damage and stun the target for 1.25 seconds.', '', 'Shield of Daybreak', 'Sobafire.com'),
(401, 'leona-eclipse.png', '', ' Cooldown: 14<br />Cost: 60<br /><br />Leona raises her shield to gain 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 bonus Armor and Magic Resistance for 3 seconds. When the effect ends she deals 60 / 110 / 160 / 210 / 260 (+40% of ability power) magic damage to nearby enemies and prolongs the effect for a bonus 3 seconds if any enemies are struck.', '', 'Eclipse', 'Sobafire.com'),
(402, 'leona-zenith-blade.png', '', ' Cooldown: 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9<br />Cost: 60<br /><br />Leona projects a solar image of her sword, which deals 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 (+40% of ability power) magic damage to all enemies in a line. When the image fades, the last enemy champion struck will be immobilized for 0.5 seconds and Leona will dash to them.', '', 'Zenith Blade', 'Sobafire.com'),
(403, 'leona-solar-flare.png', '', ' Cooldown: 90 / 75 / 60<br />Cost: 100 / 150 / 200<br /><br />After a brief delay, Leona calls down a beam of solar energy dealing 150 / 250 / 350 (+80% of ability power) magic damage and slowing enemies by 80% for 1.5 seconds. Enemies in the center of the beam are stunned instead of slowed.', '', 'Solar Flare', 'Sobafire.com'),
(404, 'wukong-stone-skin.png', '', ' Range: 1400<br />Wukong&acute;s armor and magic resistance are increased by 4/6/8 for each nearby enemy champion.', '', 'Stone Skin', 'Sobafire.com'),
(405, 'wukong-crushing-blow.png', '', ' Cooldown: 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5<br />Cost: 40<br /><br />Wukong&acute;s next attack will deal 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 additional physical damage and will reduce the enemy&acute;s armor by 30% for 3 seconds. ', '', 'Crushing Blow', 'Sobafire.com'),
(406, 'wukong-decoy.png', '', ' Cooldown: 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 / 10<br />Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70<br /><br />Wukong becomes stealthed for 1.5 seconds and leaves an uncontrollable decoy that doesn&acute;t attack or move on the place he activated it. The decoy will deal 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+60% of ability power) magic damage to nearby enemies after 1.5 seconds.', '', 'Decoy', 'Sobafire.com'),
(407, 'wukong-nimbus-strike.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8<br />Cost: 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65<br /><br />Wukong dashes on a cloud toward a target enemy and sends out images to attack up to 2 additional enemies near his target, dealing 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+0.8 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to each enemy struck. He also gains a 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% attack speed bonus for 3 seconds after using this skill.', '', 'Nimbus Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(408, 'wukong-cyclone.png', '', ' Cooldown: 120 / 105 / 90<br />Cost: 100<br /><br />Wukong&acute;s staff grows outward and he spins it around for up to 4 seconds, dealing 20 / 110 / 200 (+1.0 per attack damage) damage every second and knocking up enemies once per cast. Wukong gains an additional 5% movement speed every half second for the duration of the spell, with the bonus disappearing once he stops spinning. ', '', 'Cyclone', 'Sobafire.com'),
(409, 'skarner-energize.png', '', ' Basic attacks lower the cooldowns of Skarner&acute;s abilities by 1 second against champions and 0.5 seconds against non-champions.', '', 'Energize', 'Sobafire.com'),
(410, 'skarner-crystal-slash.png', '', ' Cooldown: 3.5<br />Cost: 15<br />Range: 350<br />Skarner lashes out with his claws, dealing 25 / 40 / 55 / 70 / 85 (+0.8 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to all nearby enemies and charging himself with Crystal Energy for 5 seconds.<br /><br />If he casts Crystal Slash again while empowered by Crystal Energy, he deals 24 / 36/ 48 / 60 / 72 (+40% of ability power) bonus magic damage and slows all targets hit by 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 / 45% for 2 seconds. ', '', 'Crystal Slash', 'Sobafire.com'),
(411, 'skarner-crystalline-exoskeleton.png', '', ' Cooldown: 14<br />Cost: 60<br />Range: 20<br />Skarner receives a shield for up to 6 seconds which blocks 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+60% of ability power) damage. While the shield persists his movement speed is increased by 15 / 17 / 19 / 21 / 23% and his attack speed is increased by 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50%. ', '', 'Crystalline Exoskeleton', 'Sobafire.com'),
(412, 'skarner-fracture.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70<br />Range: 600<br />Skarner summons a blast of crystalline energy which deals 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 (+70% of ability power) magic damage to enemies struck and marks them for 6 seconds. Any further damage dealt to marked targets by Skarner will allow him to consume the mark to heal himself for 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 (+30% of ability power) health. Subsequent marks consumed will heal for 50% of the last. ', '', 'Fracture', 'Sobafire.com'),
(413, 'skarner-impale.png', '', ' Cooldown: 110 / 100 / 90<br />Cost: 100 / 125 / 150<br />Range: 125<br />Skarner suppresses an enemy champion for 1.75 seconds and deals 100 / 150 / 200 (+50% of ability power) magic damage to it. During this time, Skarner can move freely and will drag his helpless victim around with him. When the effect ends, Skarner&acute;s target will be dealt the same amount of magic damage again. ', '', 'Impale', 'Sobafire.com'),
(414, 'talon-mercy.png', '', ' Talon deals 10% additional damage with his autoattacks to any target that is slowed, stunned, immobilized or suppressed. ', '', 'Mercy', 'Sobafire.com'),
(415, 'talon-noxian-diplomacy.png', '', ' Cooldown: 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 / 4<br />Cost: 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60<br />Range: 20<br />Talon&acute;s next autoattack deals 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 (+0.3 per bonus attack damage) additional physical damage. If the target is a champion, they will bleed for 6 seconds, taking 3 / 6 / 9 / 12 / 15 (+0.2 per bonus attack damage) additional physical damage each second and revealing their location for the duration.', '', 'Noxian Diplomacy', 'Sobafire.com'),
(416, 'talon-rake.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65<br />Range: 750<br />Talon sends out a volley of daggers in a cone that then quickly return back to him. This attack deals 30 / 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 (+0.6 per bonus attack damage) physical damage every time it passes through an enemy. Additionally, the enemy is slowed by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 2 seconds.', '', 'Rake', 'Sobafire.com'),
(417, 'talon-cutthroat.png', '', ' Cooldown: 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 / 10<br />Cost: 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 / 55<br />Range: 700<br />Talon instantly appears behind his target, silencing them for 1 second and amplifying his damage against that target by 3 / 6 / 9 / 12 / 15% for 3 seconds. ', '', 'Cutthroat', 'Sobafire.com'),
(418, 'talon-shadow-assault.png', '', ' Cooldown: 60 / 50 / 40<br />Cost: 80 / 90 / 100<br />Range: 1000<br />Talon disperses a ring of blades outwards and gains stealth for up to 2.5 seconds while gaining 40% movement speed. When Talon emerges from stealth, the blades converge on his location. Each time a blade passes through an enemy, they take 120 / 190 / 260(+0.9 per bonus attack damage) physical damage. Each enemy can only be damaged once at the start of the ability and once at the end. ', '', 'Shadow Assault', 'Sobafire.com'),
(419, 'riven-runic-blade.png', '', ' Riven&acute;s abilities charge her blade, causing her to do 5 / 7 / 9 / 11 / 13 / 15 (+0.5 per bonus attack damage) bonus damage on her next autoattack. Riven can store up to 3 charges, but only expends one at a time. ', '', 'Runic Blade', 'Sobafire.com'),
(420, 'riven-broken-wings.png', '', ' Cooldown: 13<br />Range: 260<br />Riven steps forward and lashes out in a series of powerful sword slashes. This ability can be activated up to 3 times in a short period.<br /><br />1st Use/2nd Use: Deals 30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 (+0.7 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to a small area in front of her.<br /><br />3rd Use: Jumps into the air and slams downward, causing a larger impact nova that deals 30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 (+0.7 per bonus attack damage) physical damage and knocks nearby enemies back. ', '', 'Broken Wings', 'Sobafire.com'),
(421, 'riven-ki-burst.png', '', ' Cooldown: 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7<br />Range: 300<br />Riven stuns nearby enemies for 0.5 seconds and hits them for 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210 (+1.0 per bonus attack damage) physical damage.', '', 'Ki Burst', 'Sobafire.com'),
(422, 'riven-valor.png', '', ' Cooldown: 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7<br />Range: 250<br />Riven dashes forward and gains a shield that protects her from up to 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 (+1.0 per bonus attack damage) for 2.5 seconds.', '', 'Valor', 'Sobafire.com'),
(423, 'riven-blade-of-the-exile.png', '', ' Cooldown: 75 / 60 / 45<br /><br />Riven&acute;s sword reforms, giving her a bonus 20% Attack Damage, extended range on her damaging abilities and basic attacks for 15 seconds. <br /><br />While Blade of the Exile is active, Riven can reactivate the ability to activate Wind Slash, emitting a large cone shockwave that deals 80 / 120 / 160 (+0.6 per bonus attack damage) - 240 / 360 / 480 (+1.8 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to all units hit based on their missing life. ', '', 'Blade of the Exile', 'Sobafire.com'),
(424, 'xerath-ascended-form.png', '', ' Xerath receives 15% of his ability power as bonus armor.', '', 'Ascended Form', 'Sobafire.com'),
(425, 'xerath-arcanopulse.png', '', ' Cooldown: 7 / 6.5 / 6 / 5.5 / 5<br />Cost: 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 / 85<br />Range: 900<br />Fires a long-range beam of energy in a line, dealing 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235 (+60% of ability power) magic damage to all targets hit. ', '', 'Arcanopulse', 'Sobafire.com'),
(426, 'xerath-locus-of-power.png', '', ' Cooldown: 20 / 16 / 12 / 8 / 4<br /><br />Xerath anchors himself to the ground he is standing on for up to 8 seconds, increasing the range of all his spells by 400 and granting him 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30% bonus magic penetration. Upon disabling this ability, Xerath gains 35% movement speed for 2 seconds. He can deactivate the ability at any time after 0.5 seconds of casting it. ', '', 'Locus of Power', 'Sobafire.com'),
(427, 'xerath-mage-chains.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8<br />Cost: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90<br />Range: 600<br />Deals 70 / 120 / 170 / 220 / 270 (+70% of ability power) magic damage to an enemy and marks them with Unstable Magic for 3 seconds. The next spell Xerath strikes this enemy with in these 3 seconds will stun them for 1.5 seconds.', '', 'Mage Chains', 'Sobafire.com'),
(428, 'xerath-arcane-barrage.png', '', ' Cooldown: 80 / 70 / 60<br />Cost: 150 / 180 / 210<br />Range: 900<br />Calls down a blast of arcane energy, dealing 125 / 200 / 275(+60% of ability power) magic damage to all enemies in an area. May be cast another two times with no cost within the next 12 seconds before going on cooldown.', '', 'Arcane Barrage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(429, 'graves-gunslinger.png', '', ' Graves gains 1 / 2 / 3 bonus armor and magic resistance every second he remains in combat. This bonus stacks up to 10 times. Graves is considered in combat if he has dealt or received damage in the last 3 seconds.', '', 'Gunslinger', 'Sobafire.com'),
(430, 'graves-buckshot.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8<br />Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br />Range: 750<br />Graves fires three bullets in a cone, dealing 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 (+0.8 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to all enemies in their path. Enemies at close range can be hit by multiple projectiles, but each bullet beyond the first will deal only 25% damage. ', '', 'Buckshot', 'Sobafire.com'),
(431, 'graves-smoke-screen.png', '', ' Cooldown: 20 / 19 / 18 / 17 / 16<br />Cost: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90<br />Range: 700<br />Graves fires a smoke canister at the target area, dealing 60 / 110 / 160 / 210 / 260 (+60% of ability power) magic damage upon landing and creating a cloud of smoke for 5 seconds. Enemies inside the smoke cloud will be slowed by 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35% and will have their vision reduced to only what is inside the smoke cloud and enemies attacking them, everything else will look like it is in the Fog of War. ', '', 'Smoke Screen', 'Sobafire.com'),
(432, 'graves-quickdraw.png', '', ' Cooldown: 22 / 20 / 18 / 16 / 14<br />Cost: 50<br /><br />Graves dashes forward, gaining a 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80% attack speed boost for 4 seconds. Attacking enemy units with autoattacks lowers the cooldown of Quickdraw by 1 second each attack. ', '', 'Quickdraw', 'Sobafire.com'),
(433, 'graves-collateral-damage.png', '', ' Cooldown: 80 / 70 / 60<br />Cost: 100<br /><br />Graves fires an explosive shell in a straight line, dealing 250 / 375 / 500 (+1.4 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to the first target it hits. After hitting a champion or reaching the end of its range, the shell explodes dealing 140 / 275 / 400 (+1.2 per bonus attack damage) physical damage in a cone behind the target. ', '', 'Collateral Damage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(434, 'shyvana-fury-of-the-dragonborn.png', '', ' Shyvana&acute;s melee attacks enhance her abilities.<br /><br />Twin Bite - Reduces the cooldown by 0.5 seconds.<br /><br />Burnout - Extends the duration by 1 second to a maximum of 6 seconds.<br /><br />Flame Breath - Deals 20% of the ability&acute;s damage to debuffed targets.<br /><br />Dragon&acute;s Descent - Attacks generate 2 Fury and Shyvana passively gains Fury over time while in human form.', '', 'Fury of the Dragonborn', 'Sobafire.com'),
(435, 'shyvana-twin-bite.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6<br /><br />Shyvana strikes twice on her next attack. The second attack will deal 80 / 85 / 90 / 95 / 100 physical damage +% of attack damage. Both attacks trigger On-Hit effects and Fury of the Dragonborn effects.<br /><br />Dragon Form: Twin Bite cleaves all units in front of Shyvana. Each unit hit will be dealt on-hit effects and grant Fury twice. ', '', 'Twin Bite', 'Sobafire.com'),
(436, 'shyvana-burnout.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12<br /><br />During the next 3 seconds, Shyvana will deal 25 / 40 / 55 / 70 / 85 (+0.2 per bonus attack damage) magic damage each second to nearby enemies and her movement speed will be greatly increased by 30 / 35 / 40 / 40 / 50%. Shyvana&acute;s movement speed bonus itself will be reduced multiplicatively by 15% for every second that passes. <br /><br />Dragon Form: Shyvana now scorches the earth where she walks, leaving a trail of fire for 5 seconds that will continually deal magic damage to enemies that pass over it. ', '', 'Burnout', 'Sobafire.com'),
(437, 'shyvana-flame-breath.png', '', ' Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8<br /><br />Shyvana unleashes a fireball forward in a line that will hit the first enemy it hits, dealing 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260 (+0.6 per ability power) magic damage to it andreducing their armor by 15% for 4 seconds. <br /><br />Dragon Form: Flame Breath engulfs all units in a cone in front of Shyvana.', '', 'Flame Breath', 'Sobafire.com'),
(438, 'shyvana-dragons-descent.png', '', ' (Passive): Shyvana reinforces her scales, increasing her armor and magic resistance by 15 / 20 / 25. These defensive bonuses are doubled while in Dragon Form. <br /><br />(Active): Shyvana transforms into a dragon and dashes to a target location. Enemies along her path take 200 / 300 / 400 (+70% of ability power) magic damage and are pushed toward her target location. Shyvanna must have a full fury bar to use this spell. ', '', 'Dragon&acute;s Descent', 'Sobafire.com'),
(439, 'fizz-nimble-fighter.png', '', ' Fizz&acute;s dexterity allows him to ignore unit collision and take (4/6/8/10/12/14) less damage from basic attacks.', '', 'Nimble Fighter', 'Sobafire.com'),
(440, 'fizz-urchin-strike.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6<br />Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70<br />Range: 550<br />Fizz dashes a fixed distance in the direction of his target, dealing his total attack damage as physical damage plus additional 10 / 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 (+0.7 per ability power) magic damage to it. The ability will also apply on-hit effects. ', '', 'Urchin Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(441, 'fizz-seastone-trident.png', '', ' Cooldown: 10<br />Cost: 40<br /><br />(Passive): Fizz&acute;s autoattacks rend his target, dealing 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 (+0.35 per ability power) magic damage over 3 seconds that strengthens by 4 / 5 / 6 / 7 / 8 % of the target&acute;s missing health. Multiple autoattacks will only refresh the duration. <br /><br />(Active): Fizz&acute;s attacks are empowered by 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 (+0.35 per ability power) for the next 5 seconds, dealing additional magic damage on-hit and causing grievous wounds to his opponents. ', '', 'Seastone Trident', 'Sobafire.com'),
