(443, 'fizz-chum-the-waters.png', '', ' Cooldown: 150<br />Cost: 100 / 85 / 70<br />Range: 1275<br />Fizz throws a fish in a line that will bind itself onto the first enemy champion it hits. If it doesn&acute;t hit an enemy champion it will stay on an area, and it will stick to the first enemy champion that walks into the area.<br /><br />Regardless of position, after 1.5 seconds, a Shark will emerge from the earth to eat the fish, dealing 200 / 325 / 450 (+1.0 per ability power) magic damage, knocking up and slowing all enemies by 50/60/70)% in the area for 1.5 seconds. ', '', 'Chum the Waters', 'Sobafire.com'),
(444, 'viktor-evolving-technology.png', '', 'Viktor starts with a Hex Core that provides him with stats and can be upgraded in the store to augment one of his abilities. The Hex Core can only be upgraded once, and cannot be sold back to the store. ', '', 'Evolving Technology', 'Sobafire.com'),
(445, 'viktor-power-transfer.png', '', 'Viktor blasts an enemy unit for 80/125/170/215/260 (+65% of ability power) magic damage, returning 40% of the damage dealt as a shield for 3 seconds. ', '', 'Power Transfer ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(446, 'viktor-gravity-field.png', '', 'Viktor conjures a gravitational imprisonment device, slowing all enemies by 28/32/36/40/44% of their Movement Speed and stacks every 0.5 seconds. At 3 stacks the target will be stunned for 1.5 seconds. ', '', 'Gravity Field ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(447, 'viktor-death-ray.png', '', 'Viktor uses his robotic arm to fire a chaos beam that cuts across the field in a line, dealing 70/115/160/205/250 (+70% of ability power) magic damage to every enemy in its path. ', '', 'Death Ray ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(448, 'viktor-chaos-storm.png', '', 'Viktor conjures a singularity at the target location, dealing 150/250/350 (+55% of ability power) magic damage and silencing enemies in the area for 0.5 seconds.\r\n\r\nAs it churns, it deals 40/60/80 (+20% of ability power) magic damage every second to nearby enemies for 7 seconds. The storm moves faster the closer it is to Viktor.\r\n\r\nActivating this ability again while the singularity is active will redirect it. ', '', 'Chaos Storm ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(449, 'ahri-soul-eater.png', 'Bir büyü rakibe her isabet ettiğinde bir Öz Hırsızı yükü verir (büyü başına azami 3 yük). 9 yüke ulaştığında, bir sonraki büyü %35 Can Emme özelliği kazanır.', 'Ahri gains a charge of Soul Eater whenever one of her spells hits an enemy (max: 3 charges per spell). Upon reaching 9 charges, Ahri''s next spell has 35% Spell Vamp. ', 'Öz Hırsızı', 'Öz Hırsızı', 'Sobafire.com'),
(450, 'ahri-orb-of-deception.png', 'Ahri, küresini ileri fırlatıp geri çeker; küre giderken büyü hasarı, dönerken de Gerçek hasar verir.<br>\nGiderken 40/65/90/115/140 (+0.33) büyü hasarı, dönüşte 40/65/90/115/140 (+0.33) gerçek hasar verir.<br><br>\nBedel<br>\n    70/75/80/85/90 Mana<br>\nMenzil<br>\n    880 ', 'Cooldown: 7<br>\r\nCost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br>\r\nRange: 880<br>\r\n\r\nAhri throws out and pulls back her orb, dealing 40 / 65 / 90 / 115 / 140 (+33% of ability power) magic damage on the way out and 40 / 65 / 90 / 115 / 140 (+33% of ability power) true damage on the way back. ', 'Aldatan Küre', 'Aldatan Küre', 'Sobafire.com'),
(451, 'ahri-fox-fire.png', 'Ahri''nin fırlattığı üç tilki ateşi, kısa bir süre sonra yakındaki hedeflere kilitlenip saldırır.\nFırlatılan üç tilki ateşi. yakındaki rakiplere (öncelikli olarak şampiyonlara) kilitlenerek, 40/65/90/115/140 (+0.4) büyü hasarı verirler. Birden fazla tilki ateşiyle vurulan rakipler, her ilave tilki ateşinden %50 hasar alır.\n\nBedel\n    60 Mana\nMenzil\n    800 ', 'Cooldown: 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5<br>\r\nCost: 60<br>\r\nRange: 800<br>\r\n\r\nAhri releases three fox-fires, which after a short delay lock on and attack nearby enemies (prioritizes champions), dealing 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 (+38% of ability power) magic damage. Additional fox-fires that hit the same target deal 50% damage, up to a maximum total damage of 80 / 140 / 200 / 260 / 320 (+75% of ability power). ', '', 'Fox-Fire', 'Sobafire.com'),
(452, 'ahri-charm.png', '', 'Cooldown: 12<br>\r\nCost: 50 / 65 / 80 / 95 / 110<br>\r\nRange: 975<br>\r\n\r\nAhri blows a kiss that deals 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+35% of ability power) magic damage to an enemy and charms it, causing them to walk harmlessly towards her for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds. ', '', 'Charm', 'Sobafire.com'),
(453, 'ahri-spirit-rush.png', '', 'Cooldown: 80 / 70 / 60<br>\r\nCost: 100<br>\r\nRange: 450<br>\r\n\r\nAhri dashes forward and fires essence bolts, damaging 3 nearby enemies (prioritizes champions) for 100 / 140 / 180 (+30% of ability power) magic damage per bolt. Spirit Rush can be cast up to three times before going on cooldown. ', '', 'Spirit Rush', 'Sobafire.com'),
(454, 'volibear-chosen-of-the-storm.png', '', 'When Volibear''s health drops below 30% of his maximum health, he will heal for 30% of his maximum health over the next 6 seconds. This passive effect has a 120 second cooldown. ', '', 'Chosen of the Storm', 'Sobafire.com'),
(455, 'volibear-rolling-thunder.png', '', 'Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8<br>\r\nCost: 40<br>\r\nRange: 300<br>\r\n\r\nFor the next 4 seconds, Volibear will gain 45% movement speed if he is moving towards a nearby visible enemy champion. Additionally, Volibear''s next autoattack during this time will deal 25 / 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 bonus physical damage and will fling the target behind him. ', '', 'Rolling Thunder', 'Sobafire.com'),
(456, 'volibear-frenzy.png', '', 'Cooldown: 18<br>\r\nCost: 35<br>\r\nRange: 400<br>\r\n\r\nPassive: Volibear temporarily gains 8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20 % bonus attack speed after an autoattack. This bonus stacks up to 3 times and lasts for 4 seconds.<br>\r\n\r\nActive: While Volibear has 3 stacks of Frenzy, he can activate this ability to bite a target enemy. The stacks won''t be consumed. The bite will deal 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260 (+18% of bonus health) physical damage. This damage will in turn be increased by 1% for every 1 % of the target''s missing health. ', '', 'Frenzy', 'Sobafire.com'),
(457, 'volibear-majestic-roar.png', '', 'Cooldown: 11<br>\r\nCost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80<br>\r\nRange: 425<br>\r\n\r\nVolibear lets out a powerful roar that deals 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 (+60% of ability power) magic damage and slows nearby enemies by 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 % for 3 seconds. Minions, monsters and pets are feared for the duration as well. ', '', 'Majestic Roar', 'Sobafire.com'),
(458, 'volibear-thunder-claws.png', '', 'Cooldown: 100 / 90 / 80<br>\r\nCost: 100<br>\r\nRange: 300<br>\r\n\r\nFor the next 12 seconds, Volibear''s autoattacks will blast his target with lightning that will bounce to up to 3 nearby enemies. Each bolt of lightning will deal 75 / 115 / 155 (+30% of ability power) magic damage and will only hit each target once. ', '', 'Thunder Claws', 'Sobafire.com'),
(459, 'sejuani-frost.png', '', 'Sejuani''s basic attacks apply Frost, reducing enemy Movement Speed by 10% for 3 seconds.', '', 'Frost', 'Sobafire.com'),
(460, 'http://edge2.mobafire.com/images/ability/sejuani-arctic-assault.png', '', 'Cooldown: 19 / 17 / 15 / 13 / 11<br>\r\nCost: 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110<br>\r\nRange: 700<br><br>\r\n\r\nSejuani charges forward to deal 60 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210 (+40% of ability power) magic damage and apply Frost to enemies. Sejuani stops upon colliding with an enemy champion. ', '', 'Arctic Assault', 'Sobafire.com'),
