(463, 'sejuani-glacial-prison.png', '', 'Cooldown: 150 / 130 / 110<br>\r\nCost: 100<br>\r\nRange: 1150<br><br>\r\n\r\nSejuani throws her weapon, stunning the first enemy champion hit for 2 seconds. Nearby enemies are stunned for 1 second. All targets take 150 / 250 / 350 (+80% of ability power) magic damage and are affected by Frost. ', '', 'Glacial Prison', 'Sobafire.com'),
(464, 'ziggs-short-fuse.png', 'Her 12 saniyede bir Ziggs’in bir sonraki normal saldırısı ekstra büyü hasarı (magic damage) verir. Ziggs her yetenek kullanışında bu bekleme süresi azalır. ', 'Every 12 seconds, Ziggs'' next basic attack deals 13 + (7 per level) (+35% of ability power) bonus magic damage. This cooldown is reduced by 4 seconds whenever Ziggs uses an ability. ', 'Short Fuse', 'Short Fuse', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(465, 'ziggs-bouncing-bomb.png', '', 'Cooldown: 6 / 5.5 / 5 / 4.5 / 4<br>\r\nCost: 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100<br>\r\nRange: 850<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZiggs throws a bouncing bomb that deals 75 / 120 / 165 / 210 / 255 (+65% of ability power) magic damage upon hitting an enemy or after bouncing twice. ', '', 'Bouncing Bomb', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(466, 'ziggs-satchel-charge.png', '', 'Cooldown: 30 / 27 / 24 / 21 / 18<br>\r\nCost: 65<br>\r\nRange: 1000<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZiggs flings an explosive charge that detonates after 4 seconds, or when this ability is activated again. The explosion deals 70 / 105 / 140 / 175 / 210 (+35% of ability power) magic damage to enemies, knocking them away. Ziggs is also knocked away, but takes no damage. ', '', 'Satchel Charge', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(467, 'ziggs-hexplosive-minefield.png', '', 'Cooldown: 16<br>\r\nCost: 80 / 90 / 100 / 110 / 120<br>\r\nRange: 900<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZiggs scatters 11 proximity mines that detonate on enemy contact. The first mine deals 40 / 65 / 90 / 115 / 140 (+30% of ability power) magic damage and slows the enemy by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 % for 2 seconds.<br><br> Enemies who have already hit a mine will take half damage from additional mines, up to a total of 240 / 390 / 540 / 690 / 840 (+180% of ability power) possible magic damage. <br><br>The mines are visible for all players and last 10 seconds. ', '', 'Hexplosive Minefield', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(468, 'ziggs-mega-inferno-bomb.png', '', 'Cooldown: 120 / 105 / 90<br>\r\nCost: 100<br>\r\nRange: 5300<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZiggs deploys his ultimate creation, the Mega Inferno Bomb, hurling it an enormous distance. Enemies in the primary blast zone take 250 / 375 / 500 (+90% of ability power) magic damage, while those further away take 75% of that damage. ', '', 'Mega Inferno Bomb', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(469, 'nautilus-staggering-blow.png', 'Nautilius’un bir düşmana yaptığı ilk saldırı düşmanı anlık olarak sersemletir(stun), Nautilius’un bunu aynı düşmana tekrar yapabilmesi için 12 sn. geçmesi gerekir.', '', 'Staggering Blow', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(470, 'nautilus-dredge-line.png', 'Nautilius çapasını fırlatır, çapa eğer bir düşmana gelirse düşmanı kendine çeker. Eğer bölgesel bir engebeye (duvarlar – Kule – Inhibutor gibi) denk gelirse bu sefer de Nautilius oraya çekilir ve yeteneğini tekrar kullanma süresi kısalır.', '', 'Dredge Line', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(471, 'nautilus-titans-wrath.png', 'Nautilius çevresinde bir kalkan oluşturur, kalkanın gücü canına bağlı olarak artar ve kalkan aktifken Nautilius’un saldırıları etrafındaki düşmanlara zamanla büyü hasarı verir.', '', 'Titan’s Wrath', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(472, 'nautilus-riptide.png', 'Nautilius toprağı sarsar ve çevresinde şok dalgaları meydana getirir. Şok dalgaları düşmaları yavaşlatır, yavaşlama etkisi zamanla etkisini yitirir. Düşmanlar birden fazla şok dalgasına maruz kalırsa ilk dalgaya kıyasla daha az hasar görür.', '', 'Riptide', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(473, 'nautilus-depth-charge.png', 'Nautilius hedeflediği düşmana bir derinlik patlaması gönderir, bu patlama düşmana doğru seyahat ettikçe hızlanır. Eğer patlama seyahat halindeyken başka düşmanlara çarparsa onları havaya fırlatır. Hedef düşmana vardığında patlayarak düşmanı sersemletir(stun) ve onu da havaya fırlatır.', '', 'Depth Charge', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(474, 'fiora-duelist.png', 'Fiora, hasar verdiği sürece 6 saniye içerisinde sağlık yeniler. Ardı ardına gerçekleştireceği saldırılar bu yenilemenin birikmesini (stack) ve artmasını sağlayacaktır. En fazla 4 birikme gerçekleştirilebilir.', '', 'Duelist', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(475, 'fiora-lunge.png', 'Fiora hedefini vurabilmek için ileri doğru atılır ve hedefine fiziksel hasar verir. Fiora, ileri doğru atılma işlemini birkaç saniye içerisinde mana harcamadan yeniden gerçekleştirebilir.', '', 'Lunge', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(476, 'fiora-riposte.png', 'Fiora, pasif olarak Attack Damage değerini arttırır.<br><br>\r\nAktif: Fiora, bir şampiyondan ya da bir canavardan kendisine gelen bir sonraki normal saldırıyı savuşturur ve saldırı gerçekleştiren hedefe büyü hasarı olarak yansıtır.', '', 'Riposte', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(477, 'fiora-burst-of-speed.png', 'Fiora, birkaç saniyeliğine saldırı hızı kazanır. Her normal saldırısı veya Lunge yeteneği, bu yetenek aktif olduğu sürece onun hareket hızını arttırır. Hareket hızı dolum yapabilir (stack).', '', 'Burst of Speed', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(478, 'fiora-blade-waltz.png', 'Fiora, savaş bölgesinin etrafında hızlı bir şekilde hareket eder ve etrafında bulunan düşmanlara rastgele fiziksel hasar verir. Bir hedefe gerçekleştirilecek başarılı saldırı, ikinci kez gerçekleştirilecek başarılı saldırının vuracağı hasarı azaltır.', '', 'Blade Waltz', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(479, 'lulu-pix-faerie-companion.png', 'Pix kendi saldırdığı düşmanlara sihirsel enerji yıldırımları gönderir. Bu yıldırımlar güdümlüdür, ancak diğer birimler tarafından engellenebilir.', '', 'Pix, Faerie Companion', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(480, 'lulu-glitterlance.png', 'Pix ve Lulu’nun gönderdiği her enerji yıldırımı düşmanlarını yavaşlatır. Bir düşman sadece bir yıldırımdan hasar görebilir.\r\n', '', 'Glitterlance', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(481, 'lulu-whimsy.png', 'Eğer dost bir şampiyonda kullanılırsa kısa süreliğine hareket hızı ve Ability Power (AP) kazandırır. Eğer düşman bir şampiyonda kullanılırsa onları saldırı yapamayan veya büyü kullanamayan sevimli yaratıklara çevirir.', '', 'Whimsy', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(482, 'lulu-help-pix.png', 'Eğer dost bir şampiyonda kullanılırsa, Pix’e emir vererek ona kalkan kazandırır. Pix, kullanılan hedefi takip eder ve saldırılarında yardımcı olur. Eğer düşman bir şampiyonda kullanılırsa, Pix düşmana zıplar ve onlara hasar verir. Pix, hedeflenen düşmanı takip ederek onları yerini belirler.', '', 'Help, Pix!', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(483, 'lulu-wild-growth.png', 'Lulu, dost bir şampiyonu büyütür, onun yakınındaki düşmanları geriye doğru iter ve ona büyük bir miktarda ekstra sağlık (health) kazandırır. Birkaç saniye için, bu dost şampiyon yakınlardaki düşmanları yavaşlatan bir aura’ya sahip olur.\r\n', '', 'Wild Growth', '', 'Efsanelerligi.com'),
(484, 'hecarim-warpath.png', '', 'Hecarim ignores unit collision and gains attack damage equal to 10 / 12.5 / 15 / 17.5 / 20 / 22.5 / 25 % of his bonus movement speed.', '', 'Warpath', 'Sobafire.com'),
(485, 'hecarim-rampage.png', '', 'Cooldown: 4<br>\r\nCost: 25<br><br>\r\n\r\nHecarim cleaves nearby enemies dealing 50 / 85 / 120 / 155 / 190 (+0.6 per bonus attack damage) physical damage. This ability deals 50% damage to minions and monsters.<br><br>\r\n\r\nIf Hecarim damages at least one enemy unit with this attack, he gains a stack of Rampage, reducing the base cooldown of this skill by 1 second for a short duration. This effect can stack up to 2 times. ', '', 'Rampage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(486, 'hecarim-spirit-of-dread.png', '', 'Cooldown: 14<br>\r\nCost: 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90<br><br>\r\n\r\nHecarim deals 20 / 31.25 / 42.5 / 53.75 / 65 (+20% of ability power) magic damage to nearby enemies every second for 4 seconds, up to a maximum of 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260 (+80% of ability power) magic damage.<br><br> Hecarim gains health equal to 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 % of any damage those enemies suffer. Healing from damage dealt to minions is capped to 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 health. ', '', 'Spirit of Dread', 'Sobafire.com'),
(487, 'hecarim-devastating-charge.png', '', 'Cooldown: 24 / 22 / 20 / 18 / 16<br>\r\nCost: 60<br><br>\r\n\r\nHecarim gains 75% movement speed for over the course of 3 seconds. His next attack knocks the target back and deals a minimum of 40 / 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 (+0.5 per bonus attack damage) and a maximum of 80 / 150 / 220 / 290 / 360 (+1.0 per bonus attack damage) additional physical damage based on the distance he has travelled since activating the ability. ', '', 'Devastating Charge', 'Sobafire.com'),
(488, 'hecarim-onslaught-of-shadows.png', '', 'Cooldown: 140 / 120 / 100<br>\r\nCost: 100<br><br>\r\n\r\nHecarim summons spectral riders and charges forward, dealing 100 / 200 / 300 (+80% of ability power) magic damage in a line. Hecarim creates a shockwave when he finishes his charge, dealing 50 / 125 / 200 (+40% of ability power) additional magic damage to nearby enemies and causing them to flee in terror away from Hecarim for 1 second. ', '', 'Onslaught of Shadows', 'Sobafire.com'),
(489, 'varus-living-vengeance.png', '', 'On champion kill or assist, Varus gains 40% attack speed for 6 seconds.<br>\r\nOn minion kill, Varus gains 20% attack speed for 3 seconds.', '', 'Living Vengeance', 'Sobafire.com'),
(490, 'varus-piercing-arrow.png', '', 'Cooldown: 16 / 14 / 12 / 10 / 8<br>\r\nCost: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90<br><br>\r\n\r\nVarus starts drawing back his next shot, gradually increasing its range and damage, then he fires it, dealing minimum 10 / 43 / 77 / 110 / 143 (+1.0 per attack damage) to maximum 15 / 65 / 115 / 165 / 215 (+1.6 per attack damage) physical damage, reduced by 15% per enemy hit (minimum 33%).<br><br>\r\n\r\nWhile preparing to shoot, Varus cannot autoattack or use abilities, and his movement speed is slowed by 20%. After 4 seconds, Piercing Arrow fails but refunds half its mana cost. ', '', 'Piercing Arrow', 'Sobafire.com'),
(491, 'varus-blighted-quiver.png', '', 'Varus'' basic attacks deal bonus 10 / 14 / 18 / 22 / 26 (+0.25 per ability power) magic damage and apply Blight for 6 seconds (stacks 3 times).<br><br>\r\nVarus'' other abilities detonate Blight, dealing magic damage equal to 2 / 2.75 / 3.5 / 4.25 / 5% (+0.01% per ability power) of the target''s maximum health per stack.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis damage is capped against monsters. ', '', 'Blighted Quiver', 'Sobafire.com'),
(492, 'varus-hail-of-arrows.png', '', 'Cooldown: 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 / 10<br>\r\nCost: 80<br>\r\nRange: 925<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVarus fires a hail of arrows that deal 65 / 105 / 145 / 185 / 225 (+0.6 per bonus attack damage) physical damage and desecrate the ground. Desecrated ground slows enemies'' Movement Speed by 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 / 45% and reduces their healing and regeneration by 50%. ', '', 'Hail of Arrows', 'Sobafire.com'),
(493, 'varus-chain-of-corruption.png', '', 'Cost: 120<br>\r\nRange: 1075<br><br>\r\n\r\nVarus flings out a tendril of corruption that deals 150 / 250 / 350 (+1.0 per ability power) magic damage and immobilizes the first enemy champion hit for 2 seconds.<br><br>\r\nThe corruption then spreads towards nearby uninfected enemy champions, applying the same damage and immobilize if it reaches them. The corruption will continue to spread until there are no further unaffected targets in range.\r\n', '', 'Chain of Corruption', 'Sobafire.com'),
(494, 'darius-hemorrhage.png', '', 'Darius'' basic attacks and damaging abilities cause enemies to bleed for 12 / 15 / 18 / 21 / 24 / 27 / 30 / 33 / 36 (+0.4 per bonus attack damage) magic damage over 5 seconds, stacking up to 5 times.<br><br>\r\n\r\nDarius gains 5% movement speed for each bleeding enemy champion.', '', 'Hemorrhage', 'Sobafire.com'),
(495, 'darius-decimate.png', '', 'Cooldown: 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 seconds<br><br>\r\n\r\nCost: 40 mana<br><br>\r\n\r\nRange: 425<br><br>\r\nDarius swings his axe in a wide circle. Enemies struck by the blade take more damage than those struck by the shaft, taking 50% additional damage. Physical Damage: 70 / 105 / 140 / 175 / 210) (+0.7 per bonus attack damage)\r\n', '', 'Decimate', 'Sobafire.com'),
(496, 'darius-crippling-strike.png', '', 'Cooldown: 8 seconds<br><br>\r\n\r\nCost: 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 mana<br><br>\r\n\r\nRange: 300<br><br>\r\n\r\nDarius'' next basic attack deals 120 / 140 / 160 / 180 / 200% additional damage and slows the target''s movement and attack speed by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 2 seconds.<br><br>\r\n\r\nCrippling strike''s base cooldown is reduced by 1 second for each stack of Hemorrhage on the target.', '', 'Crippling Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(497, 'darius-apprehend.png', '', 'Cooldown: 24 / 21 / 18 / 15 / 12 seconds<br><br>\r\n\r\nCost: 45<br><br>\r\n\r\nRange: 550<br><br>\r\n\r\nDarius hones his axe, granting him 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25% passive armor penetration. When activated, Darius sweeps up his enemies with his axe''s hook and pulls them to him.', '', 'Apprehend', 'Sobafire.com'),
(498, 'darius-noxian-guillotine.png', '', 'Cooldown: 100 / 90 / 80 seconds<br><br>\r\n\r\nCost: 100 mana<br><br>\r\n\r\nRange: 475<br><br>\r\n\r\nDarius leaps to target enemy champion and strikes a lethal blow, dealing 160 / 250 / 340 (+0.75 per bonus attack damage) true damage. For each stack of Hemorrhage on the target, Noxian Guillotine deals an additional 20% damage up to 320 / 500 / 680 (+1.5 per bonus attack damage).<br><br>\r\n\r\nThe cooldown is refreshed if Noxian Guillotine kills the target.', '', 'Noxian Guillotine', 'Sobafire.com'),
(499, 'draven-wicked-blades.png', '', 'Draven''s critical strikes deal 30 + (4 × level) bonus physical damage over 4 seconds. Spinning Axe also causes this effect even if it does not critically strike.', '', 'Wicked Blades', 'Sobafire.com'),
(500, 'draven-spinning-axe.png', '', 'Draven''s next attack will deal an extra 45 / 55 / 65 / 75 / 85% of his attack damage as bonus damage. This axe will ricochet off the target high up into the air. If Draven catches it, he automatically readies another Spinning Axe. Draven can have two Spinning Axes at once.', '', 'Spinning Axe', 'Sobafire.com'),
(501, 'draven-blood-rush.png', '', 'Draven gains 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60% increased Movement Speed for 1.5 seconds and 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% Attack Speed for 3 seconds. The Movement Speed bonus decreases rapidly over its duration. Catching a Spinning Axe will refresh the cooldown of Blood Rush.', '', 'Blood Rush', 'Sobafire.com'),
(502, 'draven-stand-aside.png', '', 'Draven throws his axes and deals 70 / 105 / 140 / 175 / 210 (+ .5 per bonus attack damage) physical damage by throwing his axes. Enemies hit are knocked aside and slowed by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 2 seconds.', '', 'Stand Aside ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(503, 'draven-whirling-death.png', '', 'Draven hurls two massive axes dealing 175 / 275 / 375 (+ 1.1 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to each unit struck. Deals 8% less damage per unit hit, down to a minimum of 40%. This resets when Whirling Death changes direction.<br><br> Whirling Death slowly reverses direction and returns to Draven after striking an enemy champion, or upon reactivation, or upon reaching the boundaries of the map. 110/100/90 second cool-down and costs 120 mana at all levels.', '', 'Whirling Death', 'Sobafire.com'),
(504, 'jayce-p.png', '', 'Jayce gains 40 movement speed and ignores unit collision for 1.25 seconds each time Transform is cast.', '', 'Hextech Capacitor ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(505, 'jayce-q.png', '', 'To the Skies: Jayce leaps to an enemy dealing 20 / 65 / 110 / 155 / 200 (+1.0 per bonus attack damage) physical damage and slowing enemies by 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% for 2 seconds.<br><br>\r\n\r\nShock Blast: Jayce fires an orb of electricity that detonates upon hitting an enemy (or reaching the end of its path) dealing 60 / 115 / 170 / 225 / 280 (+1.2 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to all enemies in the area of the explosion. If fired through an Acceleration Gate, Shock Blast''s damage, range, speed, and explosion radius are increased by 40%.', '', 'To the Skies! / Shock Blast ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(506, 'jayce-w.png', '', 'Lightning Field: Passive: Jayce restores 6 / 8 / 10 / 12 / 14 mana per strike while in Hammer form. Active: Jayce creates a field of lightning that damages nearby enemies for 100 / 170 / 240 / 310 / 380 (+100% of ability power) magic damage per second for 4 seconds.\r\n\r\nHyper Charge: Jayce gains a burst of energy, increasing his attack speed to the maximum amount for 3 attacks. These attacks do 70 / 85 / 100 / 115 / 130% of his attack damage.', '', 'Lightning Field / Hyper Charge', 'Sobafire.com'),
(507, 'jayce-e.png', '', 'Thundering Blow: Jayce deals 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 (+1.0 per bonus attack damage) + 8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20% of targets maximum health as magic damage and knocks them back a short distance. Damage to monsters is capped at 200 / 300 / 400 / 500 / 600 magic damage.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAcceleration Gate: Jayce deploys an Acceleration Gate, which increases the movement speed of allied champions who pass through it by 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% for 3 seconds. This movement speed bonus rapidly decreases over its duration. If Shock Blast is fired through the gate, its speed, range, damage, and explosion radius are increased by 40%.', '', 'Thundering Blow / Acceleration Gate ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(508, 'jayce-r.png', '', 'Mercury Cannon: Transforms the Mercury Hammer into the Mercury Cannon gaining new abilities and increased range. The first attack in this form reduces the target''s Armor and Magic Resist by 10/15/20/25% for 5 seconds.<br><br>\r\n\r\nMercury Hammer: Transforms the Mercury Cannon into the Mercury Hammer gaining new abilities and increases Jayce''s Armor and Magic Resist by 5/15/25/35. The first attack in this form deals 20/60/100/140 additional magic damage.', '', 'Mercury Cannon / Mercury Hammer ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(509, 'zyra-p.png', '', 'Upon death, Zyra returns to her plant form. After 2 seconds, she can press any ability to fire a Vengeful Thorn towards her cursor, dealing 99 + (25 × current level) true damage to each enemy it strikes.\r\n', '', 'Rise of the Thorns', 'Sobafire.com'),
(510, 'zyra-q.png', '', 'Zyra grows a bud at target location. After a brief delay it explodes, launching damaging thorns at all nearby enemies dealing 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235 (+60% of ability power) magic damage to enemies within the area. If cast on a seed, Deadly Bloom grows a Thorn Spitter plant, which fires at enemies from afar dealing magic damage. Lasts 10 seconds.\r\n', '', 'Deadly Bloom', 'Sobafire.com'),
(511, 'zyra-w.png', '', '(Passive): Grants 4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 20% Cooldown reduction.\r\n<br><br>\r\n(Active): Zyra plants a seed, granting vision of an area for up to 30 seconds. Other spells cast on seeds will turn them into plants who fight for Zyra. They do 26 + (6 x level) (+20% of ability power) damage. Each plant attacking the same target does 50% reduced damage.\r\n<br><br>\r\nZyra stores a seed every 17 / 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 seconds and can hold up to a maximum of 2. Zyra can plant a maximum of 4 at a time.\r\n', '', 'Rampant Growth', 'Sobafire.com'),
(512, 'zyra-e.png', '', 'Zyra sends forth vines through the ground to ensnare her target, dealing 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 (+50% of ability power) magic damage and rooting enemies they come across. If cast on a seed, Grasping Roots grows a Vine Lasher, whose short range attacks reduce enemy Movement Speed.\r\n', '', 'Grasping Roots', 'Sobafire.com'),
(513, 'zyra-r.png', '', 'Zyra summons a twisted thicket at a target location, dealing 180 / 265 / 350 (+75% of ability power) magic damage to enemies as it expands and knocking them airborne as it contracts. Plants in the area are enraged, increasing their Attack Speed by 50 %.\r\n', '', 'Stranglethorns', 'Sobafire.com'),
(514, 'diana-p.png', '', 'Diana has 20% increased Attack Speed. Every third strike cleaves nearby enemies for 20 / 25 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 65 / 80 / 95 / 110 / 125 / 140 / 155 / 175 / 195 / 215 / 240 / 265 / 290 (+60% of ability power) additional magic damage.\r\n', '', 'Moonsilver Blade', 'Sobafire.com'),
(515, 'diana-q.png', '', 'Diana swings her blade to unleash a bolt of lunar energy, afflicting enemies with Moonlight for 3 seconds and dealing 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260 (+80% of ability power) magic damage in an arc before exploding.\r\n', '', 'Crescent Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(516, 'diana-w.png', '', 'Diana creates three orbiting spheres that detonate on contact with enemies to deal 20 / 36 / 52 / 68 / 84 (+20% of ability power) magic damage per orb in an area. She also gains a temporary shield that absorbs 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 / 155 (+40% of ability power) damage. This shield is refreshed if all three spheres detonate.\r\n', '', 'Pale Cascade', 'Sobafire.com'),
(517, 'diana-e.png', '', 'Diana draws in and slows all nearby enemies by 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 % for 2 seconds.\r\n', '', 'Moonfall', 'Sobafire.com');
INSERT INTO `lol_skills` (`SkillNum`, `imgPath`, `TR`, `EN`, `TR_skillname`, `EN_skillname`, `Cevirmen`) VALUES
(518, 'diana-r.png', '', 'Diana teleports to an enemy and deals 100 / 160 / 220 (+60% of ability power) magic damage. Lunar Rush has no cooldown when used to teleport to a target afflicted with Moonlight and will consume all active Moonlight debuffs.\r\n', '', 'Lunar Rush', 'Sobafire.com'),
(519, 'rengar-p.png', '', 'While in brush or stealth, Rengar will leap at the target when using his basic attack. Rengar builds 1 Ferocity with each ability he uses on enemies. When reaching 5 Ferocity, Rengar''s next ability becomes empowered, granting it a bonus effect. ', '', 'Unseen Predator', 'Sobafire.com'),
(520, 'rengar-q.png', '', 'Rengar''s next basic attack deals 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 bonus physical damage and grants him 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 % increased Attack Speed for 3 seconds.<br><br>\r\n\r\nFerocity Bonus: Rengar deals enhanced damage equal to 100% of Rengar''s Attack Damage and his Attack Speed bonus increases to 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 %. ', '', 'Savagery', 'Sobafire.com'),
(521, 'rengar-w.png', '', 'Rengar lets out a battle roar, dealing 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 (+80% of ability power) magic damage to enemies and gaining 15 / 22 / 29 / 36 / 43 bonus Armor and Magic Resist for 3 seconds.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFerocity Bonus: Rengar heals himself for 15% of his maximum health. ', '', 'Battle Roar', 'Sobafire.com'),
(522, 'rengar-e.png', '', 'Rengar throws a bola at his target, dealing 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 (+0.7 per bonus attack damage) physical damage and slowing them by 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 % for 2.5 seconds.<br><br>\r\n\r\nFerocity Bonus: Rengar initially roots the target for 1 second. The slow is applied in full after the 1 second, and decays over the remaining 1.5 seconds.', '', 'Bola Strike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(523, 'rengar-r.png', '', 'Rengar activates his predatory instincts, stealthing and revealing all enemy champions in a 2000 / 3000 / 4000 radius around him. He gains 20 / 25 / 30 % Movement Speed and rapidly generates Ferocity while stealthed.\r\n<br><br>\r\nLasts 5 seconds or until he uses an ability. ', '', 'Thrill of the Hunt ', 'Sobafire.com'),
(524, 'syndra-p.png', '', 'Each of Syndra''s normal abilities gain an extra effect at max rank.\r\n<br><br>\r\nDark Sphere: Deals 15% bonus damage against enemy Champions.<br>\r\nForce of Will: Increases the slowing duration by 33%<br>\r\nScatter the Weak: Cone width increased by 50% ', '', 'Transcendent', 'Sobafire.com'),
(525, 'syndra-q.png', '', 'Syndra conjures a dark sphere at a target location, dealing 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 (+60% of ability power) magic damage in an area. The sphere remains for 6 seconds and can be manipulated by Syndra''s other abilities.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOnce at max rank, it deals 265 (+69% of ability power) magic damage when used against enemy champions. ', '', 'Dark Sphere', 'Sobafire.com'),
(526, 'syndra-w.png', '', 'First Cast: Grabs a target dark sphere, enemy minion, or neutral monster.\r\nSecond Cast: Throw a grasped dark sphere or enemy at a target area. Enemies struck by the projectile take 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 (+70% of ability power) magic damage and are slowed by 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 % for 1.5 seconds.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOnce at max rank, the slow duration will increase to 2 seconds. ', '', 'Force of Will', 'Sobafire.com'),
(527, 'syndra-e.png', '', 'Deals 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+40% of ability power) magic damage in a cone and knocks enemies away based on how close they are to Syndra. Dark spheres within the area-of-effect are also knocked back, dealing magic damage and stunning enemies in their path for 1.5 seconds. ', '', 'Scatter the Weak', 'Sobafire.com'),
(528, 'syndra-r.png', '', 'Draws upon Syndra''s full cataclysmic power, harnessing all dark spheres to deal 90 / 135 / 180 (+20% of ability power) magic damage per sphere to an enemy champion. <br><br>This spell will cause the three spheres floating about Syndra to become active, dealing a minimum of 270 / 405 / 540 (+60% of ability power) magic damage. ', '', 'Unleashed Power', 'Sobafire.com'),
(529, 'khazix-p.png', '', 'When Kha''Zix is not visible to the enemy team, he gains Unseen Threat, causing his next basic attack against an enemy champion to deal 15 / 20 / 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 / 75 / 85 / 95 / 110 / 125 / 140 / 155 / 170 / 185 / 200 / 220 + (50% of ability power) bonus magic damage and slows by 35% for 2 seconds.\r\n<br><br>\r\nUnseen Threat lasts until consumed and has no cooldown. ', '', 'Unseen Threat', 'Sobafire.com'),
(530, 'khazix-q.png', '', 'Passive: Marks isolated targets.\r\n<br><br>\r\nActive: Deals 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 / 190 (+1.6 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to a single target. Damage against isolated targets is significantly increased to 100 / 145 / 190 / 235 / 280 (+2.4 per bonus attack damage).\r\n<br><br>\r\nEvolving claws increases damage to isolated targets by 12% of their missing health. Kha''Zix also gains 50 increased range on both Taste Their Fear and his basic attacks. ', '', 'Taste Their Fear', 'Sobafire.com'),
(531, 'khazix-w.png', '', 'Kha''Zix fires spikes that explode on contact, dealing 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235 (+0.9 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to all nearby enemies. Kha''Zix is healed by 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 (+50% of ability power) if he is within the explosion radius.\r\n<br><br>\r\nEvolving spike racks causes Void Spike to fire three projectiles in a cone. Spikes will also apply Unseen Threat to all enemies caught within the area of effect. ', '', 'Void Spike', 'Sobafire.com'),
(532, 'khazix-e.png', '', 'Kha''Zix leaps to an area, dealing 65 / 100 / 135 / 170 / 205 (+0.8 per bonus attack damage) physical damage to enemies in the area he lands.\r\n<br><br>\r\nEvolving wings increases Leap''s range dramatically and causes a kill or assists to refresh the cooldown of Leap. ', '', 'Leap', 'Sobafire.com'),
(533, 'khazix-r.png', '', 'Passive: Each rank of Void Assault allows Kha''Zix to evolve one of his active abilities, granting it an additional effect.\r\n<br><br>\r\nActive: Kha''Zix enters stealth for 1 second and gains Unseen Threat, gaining 40% movement speed. Kha''Zix can cast Void Assault again within 10 seconds after activation. There is a 2 second cooldown between each cast of Void Assault.\r\n<br><br>\r\nEvolving active camouflage allows Kha''Zix to cast Void Assault three times within 10 seconds and reduces any damage by 40% he takes while in stealth. ', '', 'Void Assault', 'Sobafire.com'),
(534, 'elise-p.png', '', 'Human Form: Elise''s Human Form spells will ready a spiderling when cast on an enemy.<br><br>\r\nSpider Form: Elise summons her spiderlings to fight by her side. Spiderlings deal physical damage and take reduced damage from multi-target abilities. ', '', 'Spider Swarm', 'Sobafire.com'),
(535, 'elise-q.png', '', 'Neurotoxin: Elise deals 50 / 95 / 140 / 185 / 230 base magic damage plus 8% of target''s current health (+2% per 100 AP) as bonus damage.\r\n\r\nVenomous Bite: Elise lunges forward and bites her target, dealing 50 / 95 / 140 / 185 / 230 base magic damage plus 8% of target''s missing health (+2% per 100 AP) as bonus damage. ', '', 'Neurotoxin / Venomous Bite', 'Sobafire.com'),
(536, 'elise-w.png', '', 'Volatile Spiderling: Elise releases a venom-gorged Spiderling that explodes after 3 seconds or when it nears a target, dealing 75 / 125 / 175 / 225 / 275 (+80% of ability power) magic damage.\r\n\r\nSkittering Frenzy: Elise and her Spiderlings passively gain 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 % Attack Speed. On activation, the Attack Speed of Elise and her Spiderlings is increased by 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 % for 3 seconds and Elise is healed by 4 (+2% of ability power) health on every attack. ', '', 'Volatile Spiderling / Skittering Frenzy', 'Sobafire.com'),
(537, 'elise-e.png', '', 'Cocoon: Elise fires a skillshot that stuns the first enemy struck for 1.5 seconds.\r\n<br><br>\r\nRappel: On enemy cast: Elise reveals nearby enemy targets, while she and her spiderlings lift up into the air, and then descend upon the target enemy.\r\nOn ground cast: Elise reveals nearby enemy targets while she and her Spiderlings lift up into the air, becoming untargetable for 2 seconds. During that time she can cast Rappel again to descend upon a nearby enemy.', '', 'Cocoon / Rappel', 'Sobafire.com'),
(538, 'elise-r.png', '', 'Spider Form: Elise transforms into a menacing spider with new abilities. While in Spider Form, Elise deals 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 (+20% of ability power) bonus magic damage on attack and gains 10 Movement Speed as well as 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 bonus Armor and Magic Resistance.\r\n<br><br>\r\nHuman Form: Elise transforms into a human form with new abilities.\r\n<br><br>\r\nEach level of her ultimate allows Elise to summon an additional spiderling up to a maximum of 2 / 3 / 4 / 5. Each spiderling deals 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 (+10% of ability power) physical damage on attack, and take 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 % damage reduction from multi-target abilities. ', '', 'Spider Form / Human Form', 'Sobafire.com'),
(539, 'zed-p.png', '', 'Whenever Zed autoattacks an enemy below 50% health, he deals an additional 6 / 8 / 10% of their maximum health as magic damage. This effect cannot occur on the same target more than once every 10 seconds. ', '', 'Contempt for the Weak', 'Sobafire.com'),
(540, 'zed-q.png', '', 'Active: Zed and his shadows throw their shurikens, each dealing 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 / 215 (100% bonus AD) physical damage to the first enemy they pass through and 60 / 88 / 116 / 144 / 172 (+80% bonus AD) physical damage enemies thereafter.\r\n\r\nLiving Shadow: Additional shurikens striking the same enemy deal 50% damage and restore energy. ', '', 'Razor Shuriken', 'Sobafire.com'),
(541, 'zed-w.png', '', 'Passive: Zed''s bonus attack damage is increased by 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25%.\r\n\r\nActive: Zed''s shadow dashes forward, remaining in place for 4 seconds. Reactivating this ability will cause Zed to switch positions with this shadow.\r\n\r\nZed''s shadow will mimic his basic abilities. If both strike the same target Zed regains 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40. Energy can only be restored once per mimicked ability.\r\n', '', 'Living Shadow', 'Sobafire.com'),
(542, 'zed-e.png', '', 'Active: Zed and his shadows create a burst of shadow, dealing 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+80% bonus AD) physical damage to nearby enemies.\r\n\r\nZed''s slash reduces the cooldown of Living Shadow by 1 second for each enemy struck. His shadows'' slashes slow enemies by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 1.5 seconds.\r\n\r\nLiving Shadow: Overlapping Shadow Slashes striking the same enemy deal no additional damage but will incur an increased slow of 30 / 37.5 / 45 / 52.5 / 60% and restore energy. ', '', 'Shadow Slash', 'Sobafire.com'),
(543, 'zed-r.png', '', 'Active: Zed becomes untargetable and dashes to target enemy champion. Upon arrival, he marks the target for death and spawns a living shadow behind the target. This shadow lasts 4 seconds and mimics Zed''s abilities. Reactivating Death Mark will cause Zed to switch positions with this shadow.\r\n\r\nAfter 3 seconds, the mark will detonate, dealing physical damage equal to 100% of Zed''s attack damage plus 20 / 35 / 50% of damage dealt of all magic and physical damage dealt to the target by Zed and his shadows while the mark was active. ', '', 'Death Mark', 'Sobafire.com'),
